ages%3B%20Lev%20Radin%2FPacific%20Press%2FLightRocket%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgov-kathy-hochul-zohran-mamdani-tax-billionaires-nyc-second-homes-2026-5%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20City's%20pied-%C3%A0-terre%20tax%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20officially%20passed.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20new%20levy%20is%20set%20to%20impact%20several%20well%20known%20billionaires%2C%20including%20Ken%20Griffin.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHere's%20how%20much%20the%20Citadel%20CEO%2C%20who%20has%20found%20himself%20in%20Mayor%20Zohran%20Mamdani's%20crosshairs%2C%20will%20owe.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENew%20York%20officials%20rolled%20out%20the%20details%20of%20the%20city's%20new%20pied-%C3%A0-terre%20tax%20this%20week%2C%20so%20we%20took%20out%20our%20calculators%20and%20got%20busy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tax%20will%20impact%20an%20estimated%2010%2C000%20properties%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20including%20those%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fken-griffin-citadel-real-estate-portfolio-nyc-penthouse-homes-photos-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKen%20Griffin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20has%20found%20himself%20at%20the%20center%20of%20the%20discourse%20about%20the%20levy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmamdani-nyc-pied-a-terre-tax-hit-billionaires-bezos-griffin-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMayor%20Zohran%20Mamdani%3C%2Fa%3E%20announced%20the%20tax%20in%20April%2C%20he%20called%20out%20Griffin%20by%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Citadel%20CEO%2C%20who%20lives%20full-time%20in%20Miami%2C%20owns%20three%20apartments%20in%20New%20York%20City%3A%20a%20penthouse%20on%20Central%20Park%20South%20that%20broke%20records%20when%20he%20bought%20it%20for%20%24240%20million%20in%202019%20and%20two%20units%20in%20the%20upscale%20Upper%20East%20Side%20coop%20740%20Park%20Avenue%2C%20which%20he%20spent%20a%20total%20of%20%2483%20million%20on%20over%20the%20past%20year%20and%20a%20half.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20units%20will%20cost%20Griffin%2C%20who%20is%20estimated%20to%20be%20worth%20%2448.3%20billion%2C%20an%20extra%20%241.3%20million%20to%20%241.4%20million%20next%20year%2C%20based%20on%20the%20details%20of%20the%20tax%20outlined%20in%20the%20State's%20budget%2C%20public%20real%20estate%20records%2C%20and%20building%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hedge%20fund%20titan%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGriffin's%20Central%20Park%20South%20unit%20would%20make%20up%20the%20bulk%20of%20his%20tax%20bill%2C%20given%20its%20market%20value%20of%20%2415.55%20million%20last%20year.%20The%20Park%20Avenue%20units%2C%20which%20are%20part%20of%20a%20co-op%20building%2C%20have%20a%20combined%20market%20value%20of%20around%20%246.2%20million%2C%20based%20on%20his%20ownership%20stake%20in%20the%20building's%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20York%20City%20Department%20of%20Finance%20has%20a%20history%20of%20significantly%20underestimating%20apartment%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20assessed%20value%20has%20very%20little%20connection%20to%20actual%20market%20value%2C%26quot%3B%20Jonathan%20Miller%2C%20the%20director%20of%20markets%20for%20StreetMatrix%20and%20an%20expert%20appraiser%2C%20said.%20The%20value%20assessed%20for%20a%20%245%20million%20property%2C%20he%20said%2C%20is%20%26quot%3Bhardly%20ever%205%20million.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fzohran-mamdani-kathy-hochul-proposed-tax-nyc-explain-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enew%20tax%20code%3C%2Fa%3E%20hopes%20to%20address%20this%20over%20the%20next%20two%20years%2C%20at%20which%20point%20the%20calculus%20for%20Griffin's%20bill%20is%20set%20to%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20the%20law%20addresses%20the%20assessed-value%20disparity%20for%20condos%20and%20co-ops%20by%20levying%20a%20maximum%206.5%25%20rate%20on%20that%20value%3B%20single-family%20homes%20are%20subject%20to%20rates%20of%200.8%25%2C%201.05%25%2C%20and%201.3%25%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20home's%20value.%20The%20idea%20is%20that%2C%20over%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20next%20two%20years%2C%20the%20city%20will%20create%20its%20own%20assessment%20mechanism%20to%20more%20accurately%20capture%20market%20value.%20Once%20the%20new%20value%20is%20on%20the%20books%2C%20all%20pieds-a-terre%20will%20be%20taxed%20at%20the%20rates%20ranging%20from%200.8%25%20to%201.3%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGriffin%20is%20one%20of%20several%20well-known%20billionaires%20who%20will%20owe%20money%20under%20the%20new%20tax%20law%2C%20which%20takes%20effect%20on%20July%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20Starbucks%20CEO%20Howard%20Schultz%2C%20who%20moved%20from%20Washington%20state%20to%20Miami%20this%20year%2C%20owns%20a%20West%20Village%20penthouse%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-criticizes-mamdanis-proposed-nyc-tax-on-rich-homeowners-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20lives%20in%20D.C.%20and%20votes%20in%20Florida%2C%20owns%20property%20in%20his%20hometown%20of%20New%20York%2C%20including%20his%20Fifth%20Avenue%20triplex%20in%20the%20Trump%20Tower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Griffin%20has%20come%20out%20against%20the%20tax%20and%20the%20mayor%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BMamdani%20has%20made%20it%20very%20clear%2C%20New%20York%20does%20not%20welcome%20success%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20May%20%E2%80%94%20Amazon%20cofounder%20Jeff%20Bezos%20was%20more%20open%20to%20the%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20pied-a-terre%20tax%20is%20a%20fine%20thing%20for%20New%20York%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Bezos%20told%20CNBC%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20good%20thing%2C%20too.%20Bezos%2C%20a%20Miami%20resident%2C%20owns%20at%20least%20five%20apartments%20inside%20212%20Fifth%20Avenue%20that%20he%20purchased%20for%20a%20total%20of%20more%20than%20%24100%20million%2C%20so%20he%20should%20be%20getting%20his%20checkbook%20ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fken-griffin-pay-mamdani-nyc-pied-a-terre-tax-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780134961000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a19b7832ab5f9757add6694%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fken-griffin-pay-mamdani-nyc-pied-a-terre-tax-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22New%20York%20City's%20tax%20on%20second%20homes%20is%20now%20in%20effect%20after%20backlash%20from%20billionaires%2C%20including%20the%20Citadel%20CEO.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mberg%40businessinsider.com%20(Madeline%20Berg%2CJuliana%20Kaplan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20confined%20Pakistan%20navy%20to%20its%20ports%20during%20Operation%20Sindoor%3A%20Rajnath%20Singh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780134725000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131407257%2Cimgsize-1027160.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fdefence%2Fnews%2Findia-confined-pakistan-navy-to-its-ports-during-operation-sindoor-rajnath-singh%2Farticleshow%2F131407081.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Defence%20minister%20Rajnath%20Singh%20revealed%20the%20Indian%20Navy's%20decisive%20role%20in%20Operation%20Sindoor%2C%20keeping%20Pakistan's%20navy%20confined%20to%20ports.%20Speaking%20at%20the%20Lucknow%20naval%20museum%20inauguration%2C%20he%20highlighted%20the%20operation's%20success%20following%20the%20Pahalgam%20terror%20attack.%20Singh%20also%20lauded%20India's%20growing%20defence%20manufacturing%20and%20export%20capabilities.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A100%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22One%20way%20companies%20are%20making%20AI%20backlash%20worse%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Job%20seekers%20wait%20in%20line%20to%20enter%20an%20auditorium%20for%20a%20job%20fair%20hosted%20by%20the%20Cook%20County%20government%20to%20support%20federal%20workers%20in%20Chicago%2C%20Illinois%2C%20US%2C%20on%20Thursday%2C%20June%2026%2C%202025.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1a073db4fb977f35982184%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECEOs%20often%20tell%20workers%20to%20embrace%20AI%2C%20yet%20sometimes%20cite%20the%20technology%20when%20cutting%20jobs.%3Cp%3EJamie%20Kelter%20Davis%2FBloomberg%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMany%20CEOs%20advocate%20AI%20adoption%20yet%20cite%20it%20as%20a%20driver%20of%20layoffs%2C%20creating%20a%20complex%20workplace%20dynamic.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20company%2C%20Standard%20Chartered%2C%20said%20it%20plans%20to%20cut%20over%207%2C000%20jobs%20by%202030%20as%20tech%20takes%20on%20tasks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDespite%20CEOs'%20enthusiasm%20for%20AI%2C%20many%20firms%20are%20still%20working%20to%20see%20major%20ROI%20on%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECEOs%20want%20you%20to%20embrace%20AI.%20Many%20are%20also%20citing%20it%20as%20a%20reason%20for%20job%20cuts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20disconnect%20is%20becoming%20harder%20for%20some%20to%20ignore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELis%20Cooper%2C%20a%2030-year-old%20in%20Melbourne%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdata-analyst-quit-job-over-concerns-ai-would-replace-them-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erecently%20left%20their%20job%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20data%20analyst%20after%20growing%20uneasy%20about%20AI.%20The%20tools%20they%20were%20asked%20to%20use%20weren't%20as%20effective%20as%20humans%20so%20far%2C%20Cooper%20said%2C%20yet%20every%20interaction%20felt%20like%20contributing%20to%20technology%20that%20could%20eventually%20replace%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20an%20impossible%20situation%20to%20navigate%2C%26quot%3B%20Cooper%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAcross%20industries%2C%20execs%20are%20encouraging%20workers%20to%20embrace%20AI%20via%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartups-hackathons-ai-talent-big-tech-jobs-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehackathons%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20trainings%2C%20and%20performance%20reviews%20that%20score%20AI%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20many%20tech%20companies%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-power-list%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleading%20the%20AI%20push%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-giants-keep-axing-tech-jobs-layoffs-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannouncing%20layoffs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20reorgs%2C%20and%20hiring%20slowdowns%2C%20often%20while%20pointing%20to%20efficiency%20gains%20or%20funneling%20resources%20toward%20AI.%20Those%20moves%20could%20backfire%20by%20making%20employees%20more%20fearful%20and%20less%20willing%20to%20embrace%20the%20technology%2C%20workplace%20observers%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20major%20companies%20including%20Snap%2C%20Block%2C%20and%20Cisco%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flist-companies-replacing-human-employees-with-ai-layoffs-workforce-reductions%23ibm-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etied%20job%20cuts%20to%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20month%2C%20Meta%20laid%20off%20about%208%2C000%20employees%2C%20saying%20the%20cuts%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-is-blunt-about-need-to-cut-workers-fund-investments-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eoffset%20%26quot%3Bother%20investments%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20was%20making.%20The%20message%20was%20clear%3A%20Funding%20tech%20spending%20would%20require%20trimming%20workers.%20Meta%20also%20said%20that%20it%20was%20shifting%20more%20than%207%2C000%20employees%20onto%20AI-focused%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20changes%20%26quot%3Binclude%20layoffs%2C%20open%20role%20closures%2C%20and%20moving%20thousands%20of%20employees%20to%20business%20critical%20priorities%20across%20the%20company%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20employers%20are%20pushing%20workers%20toward%20AI%2C%20there%20is%20bubbling%20pessimism%20about%20the%20tech's%20potential%20to%20reshape%20the%20workforce.%20In%20an%20Economist%2FYouGov%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyougov.com%2Fen-us%2Farticles%2F54762-most-americans-say-artificial-intelligence-ai-development-moving-too-fast-twice-as-many-ai-pessimists-as-ai-optimists-may-9-11-2026-economist-yougov-poll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurvey%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20about%201%2C500%20US%20adults%20released%20in%20May%2C%20about%20three-quarters%20said%20they%20were%20at%20least%20somewhat%20worried%20about%20AI%20taking%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorkers%20are%20often%20far%20more%20skeptical%20about%20AI%20than%20executives%20are%2C%20largely%20because%20staffers%20fear%20it%20could%20put%20their%20jobs%20at%20risk%2C%20said%20Mark%20Ma%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Pittsburgh%20School%20of%20Business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMa%20was%20part%20of%20a%20research%20team%20that%20analyzed%20more%20than%2020%20million%20Glassdoor%20reviews%20and%20thousands%20of%20corporate%20earnings%20calls%20to%20compare%20how%20workers%20and%20C-suite%20bigwigs%20talk%20about%20AI.%20The%20takeaway%3A%20Employers%20that%20pair%20AI%20rollouts%20with%20job%20cuts%20risk%20undermining%20the%20productivity%20gains%20they%20hope%20to%20achieve%20because%20workers'%20layoff%20fears%20can%20discourage%20them%20from%20embracing%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20job%20security%20concern%20really%20dominates%2C%26quot%3B%20Ma%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20so%20big%20that%20even%20with%20such%20significant%20benefits%2C%20most%20employees%20are%20still%20resisting%20actually%20using%20AI%20or%20learning%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20resistance%20was%20on%20full%20display%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudents-boo-eric-schmidt-google-ceo-ai-university-arizona-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eseveral%20commencement%20addresses%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20month%2C%20as%20speakers%20drew%20boos%20from%20students%20facing%20a%20tough%20job%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20perceived%20threat%20of%20AI%20can%20be%20particularly%20intense%20for%20people%20who%20closely%20tie%20their%20identities%20to%20their%20work%2C%20said%20Wendy%20Turner-Williams%2C%20cofounder%20and%20chief%20data%20%26amp%3B%20AI%20officer%20at%20SymphraAI%2C%20an%20AI%20consulting%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20rejecting%20the%20tone-deafness%20of%20leaders%20who%20talk%20about%20AI%20like%20it's%20a%20productivity%20miracle%2C%20while%20it's%20the%20workers%20who%20experience%20job%20loss%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223900adeb-2463-49af-adff-c3cafa17e901%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'This%20new%20world'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pushback%20comes%20as%20some%20leaders%20are%20getting%20frank%20about%20the%20reshuffling%20underway%20at%20their%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20month%2C%20Standard%20Chartered%20said%20it%20would%20cut%20more%20than%207%2C000%20jobs%20by%202030%2C%20as%20the%20UK%20bank%20seeks%20to%20replace%20what%20group%20CEO%20Bill%20Winters%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Blower-value%20human%20capital%2C%26quot%3B%20with%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20message%20rankled%20some%20workers%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstandard-chartered-ceo-sorry-lower-value-human-capital-ai-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWinters%20later%20apologized%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20LinkedIn%20for%20his%20word%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWinters%20%26quot%3Bhas%20long%20been%20clear%20about%20the%20need%20to%20transform%20our%20workplace%20into%20a%20skills-led%20organization%20that%20offers%20our%20people%20future%20opportunities%20in%20higher%20skill%2C%20long-term%20employment%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20hardly%20alone%20in%20thinking%20AI%20could%20take%20on%20some%20work%20people%20now%20do.%20In%20a%20global%20survey%20of%20825%20execs%20by%20the%20consulting%20firm%20Mercer%20in%20October%2C%2099%25%20of%20C-suite%20leaders%20said%20they%20expect%20AI%20to%20translate%20to%20at%20least%20some%20job%20cuts%20in%20the%20next%20two%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELately%2C%20some%20executives%20have%20tempered%20the%20AI%20doomsaying.%20OpenAI's%20Sam%20Altman%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-ai-jobs-prediction-wrong-white-collar-openai-australia-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edelighted%20to%20be%20wrong%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20effect%20AI%20has%20had%20on%20entry-level%20desk%20jobs.%20And%20Nvidia%20chief%20Jensen%20Huang%20recently%20dismissed%20some%20CEOs'%20take%20that%20AI%20will%20cause%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-predictions-ai-dario-amodei-elon-musk-unemployment-humanity-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebloodbath%20in%20the%20job%20market%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20leaders%20don't%20set%20out%20to%20swap%20workers%20for%20AI%2C%20said%20Larry%20Gadea%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECEO%20and%20founder%20of%20workplace%20software%20company%20Envoy.%20The%20goal%2C%20especially%20for%20venture-backed%20companies%2C%20is%20instead%20to%20win%20in%20the%20marketplace%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20are%20trying%20to%20determine%20%26quot%3Bwho's%20going%20to%20fit%20in%20in%20this%20new%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20and%20that%20will%20be%20defined%20by%20how%20willing%20people%20are%20to%20embrace%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d3ac2ad4-a7d5-43f8-b88c-fd292d31d8d5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESurveillance%2C%20scrutiny%2C%20and%20AI%20pressure%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20some%20companies%2C%20the%20pressure%20to%20adopt%20AI%20is%20showing%20up%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-track-software-engineers-ai-use-dashboards-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworkers'%20check-ins%20with%20managers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-employee-ai-adoption-non-technical-software-engineer-performance-review-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eperformance%20reviews%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20are%20more%20tools%20to%20track%20AI%20use%20and%20public%20dashboards%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftokenmaxxing-ai-token-leaderboards-debate-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erank%20top%20performers%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Meta%2C%20some%20criticized%20the%20company's%20decision%20to%20install%20software%20on%20its%20US%20workers'%20computers%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-new-ai-tool-tracks-staff-activity-sparks-concern-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etracks%20keystrokes%20and%20mouse%20movements%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20train%20AI%2C%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Meta%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20AI%20agents%20need%20real%20examples%20of%20how%20people%20use%20computers%20and%20that%20the%20company%20has%20safeguards%20to%20protect%20sensitive%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies'%20push%20to%20get%20workers%20using%20AI%20comes%20as%20many%20of%20the%20dramatic%20productivity%20gains%20executives%20expected%20from%20the%20technology%20have%20yet%20to%20materialize%2C%20said%20Swagatam%20Basu%2C%20a%20senior%20director%20analyst%20at%20the%20consulting%20firm%20Gartner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20many%20companies%20underestimated%20how%20difficult%20it%20would%20be%20to%20integrate%20AI%20effectively%20into%20daily%20workflows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20challenge%20of%20getting%20AI%20to%20work%20is%20creating%20friction%20inside%20some%20companies.%20A%20little%20over%20half%20of%20respondents%20to%20a%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgo.writer.com%2Fai-adoption-enterprise-2026%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esurvey%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Writer%20and%20Workplace%20Intelligence%2C%20which%20included%201%2C200%20business%20leaders%20in%20five%20countries%2C%20said%20adopting%20AI%20is%20%26quot%3Btearing%20their%20company%20apart.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20bright%20spot%20for%20worried%20workers%20is%20that%20not%20all%20companies%20are%20looking%20to%20cut%20staff.%20At%20many%20firms%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20midsize%20ones%20%E2%80%94%20leaders%20are%20often%20hesitant%20to%20make%20deep%20workforce%20reductions%20because%20growth%20still%20depends%20on%20experienced%20employees%20and%20institutional%20knowledge%2C%20said%20Jivka%20Batchvarova%2C%20a%20managing%20principal%20at%20advisory%20firm%20Baker%20Tilly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20still%20going%20to%20need%20the%20humans%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20you%20feel%20about%20using%20AI%20at%20work%3F%20Let%20us%20know%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%2F%2Fembed.typeform.com%2Fnext%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20data-tf-live%3D%5C%2201KSTRK81BDRRJKPH7ZRM4CK06%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceos-cite-ai-for-job-cuts-while-urging-worker-adoption-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780134481000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1a0763b4fb977f35982186%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceos-cite-ai-for-job-cuts-while-urging-worker-adoption-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22CEOs%20are%20pushing%20workers%20to%20embrace%20AI.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20some%20are%20citing%20the%20technology%20as%20a%20reason%20for%20layoffs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tparadis%40businessinsider.com%20(Tim%20Paradis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Perplexity%20is%20giving%20out%20tech's%20latest%20status%20symbol%3A%20a%20Mac%20Mini%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225222%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mac%20Mini%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a19ceccb4fb977f35981d37%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222938%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Mac%20Mini%20is%20seeing%20a%20spike%20in%20demand.%3Cp%3EPhil%20Barker%2FFuture%20Publishing%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPerplexity%20sent%20Mac%20Minis%20to%20tech%20enthusiasts%20to%20test%20its%20AI-powered%20Personal%20Computer%20software.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDemand%20for%20Apple's%20Mac%20Mini%20has%20been%20surging%20as%20AI%20tools%20like%20OpenClaw%20gain%20popularity.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EApple%20has%20struggled%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20the%20desktop%20computer's%20newfound%20status.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPerplexity%20is%20gifting%20tech%20enthusiasts%20the%20industry's%20hottest%20commodity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDemand%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-599-m4-mac-mini-sold-out-online-us-demand-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMac%20Mini%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20going%20wild%20as%20AI%20tools%20take%20off%2C%20making%20it%20tough%20to%20g