%20Minis%20to%20people%20%26quot%3Binterested%20in%20getting%20the%20maximum%20use%20case%20out%20of%20Personal%20Computer%20in%20the%20Perplexity%20Mac%20app.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeveraging%20the%20power%20of%20social%20media%20influencers%20isn't%20uncommon%20in%20consumer%20electronics.%20Some%20companies%20send%20out%20packages%20for%20content%20creators%20to%20unbox%20online%20and%20review%20for%20their%20followers%2C%20as%20Meta%20did%20with%20its%20Ray-Ban%20smart%20glasses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerplexity%20touted%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20Mac%20Mini%20as%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20best%20ways%20to%20experience%20Personal%20Computer%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20an%20April%20blog%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20a%20mini%2C%20Personal%20Computer%20stays%20available%2024%2F7%20for%20work%20that%20needs%20a%20persistent%20machine%20or%20secure%20local%20access%20to%20your%20files%20and%20native%20apps%2C%26quot%3B%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20AI%20startup%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJesse%20Dwyer%2C%20Perplexity's%20chief%20communications%20officer%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20he%20uses%20his%20Mac%20Mini%20constantly%2C%20operating%20it%20from%20his%20other%20Apple%20devices%20whenever%20and%20wherever.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerplexity%20joins%20a%20wave%20of%20techies%20gushing%20over%20the%20Mac%20Mini%20because%20of%20its%20ability%20to%20run%20AI%20tools%2C%20like%20OpenClaw%20and%20Personal%20Computer.%20Apple%20CEO%20Tim%20Cook%20highlighted%C2%A0its%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmac-mini-demand-soars-ai-ceo-tim-cook-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eheightened%20demand%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20capabilities%20during%20a%20March%20earnings%20call.%20The%20company%20has%20struggled%20to%20keep%20the%20device%20on%20shelves%20in%20recent%20weeks%20as%20more%20tech%20users%20catch%20on%20to%20the%20hype.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-raises-mac-mini-starting-price-799-ai-boosts-demand-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estarting%20price%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20Mac%20Mini%20on%20Apple's%20website%20rose%20in%20early%20May%20to%20%24799%20for%20a%20model%20with%20512GB%20of%20storage%2C%20after%20the%20%24599%20base%20model%20with%20256GB%20of%20storage%20was%20no%20longer%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20AI%20agents%20become%20more%20capable%2C%20the%20Mac%20Mini%20is%20emerging%20as%20a%20status%20symbol%20among%20power%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fperplexity-gifts-mac-minis-in-push-for-personal-computer-tool-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780134361000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a19cee3b4fb977f35981d3b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fperplexity-gifts-mac-minis-in-push-for-personal-computer-tool-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Perplexity%20is%20sending%20out%20Mac%20Minis%20for%20people%20to%20test%20its%20new%20Personal%20Computer%20technology%20with.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jhart%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Hart)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20couple%20got%20burned%20out%20pursuing%20FIRE.%20They%20found%20another%20path%20that%20let%20them%20cut%20back%20at%20work%20and%20still%20enjoy%20life.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225378%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22andy%20hill%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a171ec42e5a80cfe04ff4c6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223590%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAndy%20Hill%20and%20Nicole%20Hill%20pivoted%20to%20Coast%20FIRE%20after%20attempting%20traditional%20FIRE.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Andy%20and%20Nicole%20Hill%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAndy%20and%20Nicole%20Hill%20struggled%20to%20find%20balance%20and%20%26quot%3Benjoy%20today%26quot%3B%20while%20pursuing%20traditional%20FIRE.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThey%20eventually%20switched%20to%20Coast%20FIRE%2C%20a%20more%20flexible%20version%20of%20the%20FIRE%20movement.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20strategy%20allows%20people%20to%20reduce%20or%20stop%20retirement%20contributions%20once%20their%20portfolio%20is%20large%20enough%20to%20grow%20on%20its%20own.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Andy%20Hill%20first%20came%20across%20the%20FIRE%20movement%20through%20podcasts%2C%20it%20seemed%20to%20offer%20a%20solution%20to%20a%20major%20problem%20in%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20felt%20so%20passionate%20about%20leaving%20my%20corporate%20job.%20I%20was%20missing%20out%20on%20my%20kids%20growing%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Hill%2C%20whose%20marketing%20career%20involved%20long%20days%20and%20travel%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThe%20solution%20that%20I%20had%20found%20was%20the%20FIRE%20movement.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20core%20principles%20of%20the%20financial%20independence%2C%20retire%20early%20movement%20%E2%80%94%20disciplined%20saving%20and%20consistent%20investing%20%E2%80%94%20aligned%20with%20his%20strengths.%20As%20a%20goal-oriented%20person%2C%20Hill%20said%2C%20he%20appreciated%20that%20FIRE%20offered%20a%20clear%20roadmap%3A%20save%20a%20majority%20of%20your%20income%20and%20invest%20it%20in%20low-cost%20index%20funds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20jacked%20up%20about%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20thought%2C%20'Max%20out%20your%20401(k)%3F%20I%20can%20do%20that.%20Check.%20Max%20out%20your%20Roth%20IRA%3F%20I%20can%20do%20that.%20Check.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20problem%20was%20that%20he%20hadn't%20fully%20discussed%20the%20FIRE%20lifestyle%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20Nicole%2C%20who%20began%20to%20feel%20the%20trade-offs.%20Maxing%20their%20retirement%20accounts%20meant%20they%20couldn't%20max%20out%20other%20areas%20of%20their%20lives%20%E2%80%94%20things%20like%20hiring%20a%20housekeeper%2C%20paying%20for%20subscriptions%20they%20enjoyed%2C%20or%20going%20out%20to%20dinner%20when%20they%20wanted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20started%20to%20slowly%20see%20that%20my%20maxing%20of%20future%20wealth%20was%20taking%20away%20current%20enjoyment%2C%26quot%3B%20Hill%20said.%20She%20was%20on%20board%20with%20creating%20time%20freedom%2C%20but%20not%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20%26quot%3Bhating%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tension%20led%20to%20a%20string%20of%20financial%20disagreements%20that%20eventually%20culminated%20in%20what%20Hill%20calls%20%26quot%3Bour%20volcano%20fight.%26quot%3B%20After%20that%2C%20they%20knew%20they%20had%20to%20make%20a%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c3553d0b-aa38-4f66-8f94-93724c0eef0f%5C%22%3EPivoting%20to%20Coast%20FIRE%3A%20A%20'middle%20ground'%20strategy%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Hills'%20compromise%20was%20to%20pivot%20to%20an%20offshoot%20of%20the%20FIRE%20movement%2C%20Coast%20FIRE.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHill%20describes%20Coast%20FIRE%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bmiddle%20ground%26quot%3B%20strategy%20%E2%80%94%20a%20way%20to%20capture%20some%20of%20the%20benefits%20of%20financial%20independence%2C%20like%20stepping%20back%20from%20a%20demanding%20corporate%20career%2C%20without%20the%20aggressive%20savings%20requirements%20of%20traditional%20FIRE.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECoast%20FIRE%20involves%20front-loading%20your%20investments.%20The%20idea%20is%20to%20build%20a%20portfolio%20large%20enough%20that%2C%20if%20left%20untouched%2C%20it%20can%20grow%20through%20compound%20interest%20and%20eventually%20reach%20your%20retirement%20goal%20without%20additional%20contributions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you%20hit%20your%20Coast%20FIRE%20number%2C%20you%20can%20reduce%20or%20stop%20saving%20for%20retirement%20and%20redirect%20that%20money%20toward%20other%20priorities.%20You'll%20still%20need%20to%20bring%20in%20income%20to%20cover%20your%20day-to-day%20expenses%2C%20but%20the%20heavy%20lifting%20of%20funding%20retirement%20is%20already%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221680%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22andy%20hill%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a19e6302e5a80cfe0500f80%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221120%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHill%20quit%20his%20corporate%20job%20in%202020%20to%20focus%20on%20his%20own%20business%2C%20Marriage%20Kids%20and%20Money.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Andy%20Hill%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20a%20compound%20interest%20calculator%2C%20the%20Hills%20determined%20they%20would%20need%20about%20%24550%2C000%20invested%20by%20age%2040%20to%20reach%20Coast%20FIRE.%20Assuming%20a%206%25%20annual%20rate%20of%20return%2C%20that%20balance%20could%20grow%20to%20roughly%20%242%20million%20by%20retirement%20age.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20that%20was%20plenty%20for%20us%20to%20live%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20Hill%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Hills%20had%20already%20done%20much%20of%20the%20heavy%20lifting%20through%20years%20of%20aggressive%20saving%20and%20investing.%20By%20around%202020%2C%20they%20had%20reached%20their%20target%20and%20began%20scaling%20back%20their%20retirement%20contributions%20before%20eventually%20stopping%20them%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20so%2C%20their%20portfolio%20has%20continued%20to%20grow%2C%20said%20Hill%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20balance%20has%20grown%20from%20around%20%24550%2C000%20in%202021%20when%20we%20stopped%20to%20closer%20to%20%241%20million%20without%20any%20further%20contributions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20confirmed%20the%20couple's%20near-seven-figure%20portfolio%20by%20reviewing%20screenshots%20of%20their%20Vanguard%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReaching%20Coast%20FIRE%20has%20completely%20changed%20the%20Hills'%20lifestyle.%20Andy%20left%20his%20corporate%20job%20in%202020%20and%20went%20all-in%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarriagekidsandmoney.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMarriage%20Kids%20and%20Money%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20personal%20finance%20platform%20he%20started%20as%20a%20blog%20in%202016.%20He%20now%20aims%20to%20work%20just%2020%20to%2025%20hours%20a%20week%20and%2C%20more%20recently%2C%20has%20limited%20his%20schedule%20to%20Tuesdays%20through%20Thursdays.%20Nicole%20has%20adopted%20a%20similar%20schedule.%20She%20works%20part-time%20as%20an%20aesthetician%20on%20Tuesdays%2C%20Thursdays%2C%20and%20Fridays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20both%20been%20doing%20this%20three-day%20workweek%2C%20and%20it%20has%20been%20fantastic%20for%20our%20marriage%2C%26quot%3B%20Hill%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20spend%20a%20lot%20more%20time%20together.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20Hill%20said%20he's%20never%20felt%20healthier%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20on%20some%20cholesterol%20meds%2C%20and%20now%20my%20doctor%20says%20I%20don't%20need%20them%20anymore.%20I%20feel%20fantastic%2C%20and%20it's%20because%20we've%20given%20ourselves%20this%20margin%20in%20life%20where%20we're%20not%20rushing%20from%20thing%20to%20thing%20to%20thing.%20We%20have%20time%20to%20think%20about%20what's%20best%20for%20us.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraditional-fire-vs-coast-fire-financial-independence-retire-early-investing-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780134301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a19e5abb4fb977f35981ef6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraditional-fire-vs-coast-fire-financial-independence-retire-early-investing-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22One%20couple%20shares%20why%20they%20ditched%20the%20FIRE%20movement%20and%20pivoted%20to%20a%20more%20flexible%20strategy%3A%20Coast%20FIRE.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kelkins%40businessinsider.com%20(Kathleen%20Elkins)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Arun%20Govil%20speaks%20on%20backlash%20over%20Ranbir's%20Ramayana%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780134267000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131407203%2Cimgsize-26414.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fnobody-wants-to-see-another-ram-arun-govil-speaks-on-backlash-over-ranbir-kapoors-ramayana-calls-him-good-actor%2Farticleshow%2F131407203.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F131407203.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EVeteran%20actor%20Arun%20Govil%2C%20who%20will%20play%20King%20Dasharath%20in%20Nitesh%20Tiwari's%20Ramayana%2C%20said%20nobody%20wants%20to%20see%20another%20Rama%2C%20explaining%20the%20backlash%20Ranbir%20Kapoor%20faced.%20However%2C%20he%20called%20Ranbir%20a%20good%20actor.%20Ranbir%20also%20revealed%20he%20will%20play%20both%20Lord%20Rama%20and%20Lord%20Parshurama%20in%20the%20film%20releasing%20on%20Diwali%202026.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20became%20a%20trailing%20spouse%20when%20I%20moved%20to%20Europe%20for%20my%20husband.%20I%20don't%20regret%20putting%20my%20family%20before%20my%20career.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221593%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lily%20Fen%20and%20her%20husband%20posing%20for%20a%20photo%20together%20in%20Prague.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a195ec72ab5f9757add60f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221195%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELily%20C.%20Fen%20followed%20her%20husband%20to%20Prague%20after%20he%20moved%20home%20in%202009.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lily%20C.%20Fen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ELily%20C.%20Fen%20met%20her%20husband%20in%20the%20Philippines%20and%20became%20a%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-canada-for-love-rebuild-my-career-identity-trailing-spouse-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrailing%20spouse%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20when%20they%20moved%20to%20Europe.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFen%20pivoted%20her%20career%20from%20acting%20to%20writing.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFen%20allowed%20her%20husband%20to%20become%20her%20provider%2C%20and%20doesn't%20regret%20putting%20family%20over%20her%20career.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202007%2C%20my%20husband's%20wanderlust%20led%20him%20from%20his%20hometown%20of%20Prague%20to%20Manila%2C%20where%20he%20and%20I%20met.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20started%20dating%2C%20he%20reassured%20me%20that%20he'd%20never%20tire%20of%20living%20in%20my%20country%2C%20but%20that%20changed%20a%20year%20later%2C%20when%20we%20took%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraveled-europe-with-baby-parental-leave-pros-cons-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etrip%20to%20Europe%3C%2Fa%3E%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20a%20drink%20with%20one%20of%20his%20former%20colleagues%2C%20who'd%20worked%20with%20him%20in%20Manila%20but%20later%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-los-angeles-mistake-came-back-london-no-regrets-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoved%20back%20to%20Europe%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20inconsequential%20%E2%82%AC6%20beer%20for%20our%20friend%20was%20more%20than%20a%20whopping%20PhP300%20for%20us.%20We%20realized%20that%20while%20this%20friend%20had%20moved%20on%20to%20earning%20a%20salary%20with%20a%20stronger%20currency%2C%20we%20weren't%20in%20as%20strong%20a%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20May%202009%2C%20he%20had%20moved%20back%20to%20Prague%20for%20more%20lucrative%20career%20opportunities.%20I%20continued%20working%20in%20the%20Philippines%2C%20where%20I%20had%20built%20my%20career%20in%20acting.%20We%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flong-distance-relationship-success-started-with-14-hour-date-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edated%20long-distance%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20before%20he%20flew%20to%20Manila%20with%20his%20family%20so%20we%20could%20exchange%20wedding%20vows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20followed%20him%20to%20Prague%20shortly%20after%2C%20full%20of%20hope%20but%20unaware%20of%20how%20many%20challenges%20awaited%20me.%20I%20had%20to%20reinvent%20myself%20in%20an%20entirely%20new%20country%20and%2C%20over%20the%20course%20of%20our%20relationship%2C%20learn%20to%20navigate%20the%20nuances%20of%20putting%20my%20family%20before%20my%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20story%20is%20part%20of%20Business%20Insider's%20ongoing%20series%2C%20%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BTrailing%20Spouses.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWe%20want%20to%20speak%20to%20people%20who%20have%20moved%20countries%20to%20support%20their%20partner's%20career.%20Please%20fill%20out%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSfjK_oTiIyG4yEjrfuR6TvwCX_-_dO524yN5h3QbOZHYSXV7Q%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dheader%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20form%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20share%20your%20experience%20with%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20won't%20publish%20any%20part%20of%20your%20submission%20without%20contacting%20you%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Faside%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228c48cc38-aa4e-428e-ae86-968863319b2b%5C%22%3ERelaunching%20my%20career%20in%20Prague%E2%80%AFcame%20with%20pleasant%20surprises%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20knew%20Prague%20would%20be%20a%20completely%20different%20city%20from%20Manila%2C%20but%20I%20hoped%20I%20could%20replicate%20my%20work%20as%20a%20performer%20over%20time.%E2%80%AF%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221146%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lily%20Fen%20and%20her%20husband%20standing%20next%20to%20a%20Christmas%20tree%20in%20a%20building%20lobby.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a1960bc2e5a80cfe050061b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22860%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFen%20chose%20to%20prioritize%20her%20family%20over%20her%20career.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lily%20C.%20Fen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20English%20speaker%2C%20the%20language%20barrier%20was%20a%20major%20hurdle.%20I%20spent%20two%20semesters%20in%20language%20classes%20developing%20a%20functional%20level%20of%20Czech.%20Prague%20had%20a%20thriving%20Czech-language%20theater%20scene%2C%20but%20I%20found%20enough%20opportunities%20where%20I%20could%20perform%20in%20English.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20my%20surprise%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprague-favorite-european-city-from-frequent-traveler%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoving%20to%20Prague%3C%2Fa%3E%20came%20with%20unique%20work%20advantages.%20While%20I'd%20done%20on-camera%20work%20in%20Manila%2C%20I%20never%20landed%20a%20commercial%20for%20a%20brand.%20Beauty%20standards%20in%20the%20Philippines%20tend%20to%20favor%20those%20with%20fairer%20skin%2C%20so%20I%20often%20lost%20roles%20to%20people%20who%20looked%20more%20Eurasian.%20In%20Prague%2C%20however%2C%20I%20found%20that%20my%20Southeast%20Asian%20heritage%20appealed%20to%20brands%20seeking%20a%20diverse%20set%20of%20actors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20booked%20a%20handful%20of%20commercials%20during%20the%20four%20years%20I%20lived%20in%20Prague%2C%20and%20it%20became%20my%20major%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffinancial-planners-clients-top-passive-income-sources-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esource%20of%20income%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20challenges%20with%20the%20language%20barrier%2C%20I%20was%20pleasantly%20surprised%20that%20I%20could%20keep%20working%20as%20a%20performer%20in%20theater%20and%20on-camera%20in%20Prague%2C%20but%20I%20had%20to%20be%20bold%20and%20proactive%20when%20it%20came%20to%20seeking%20out%20contacts%20and%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lily%20Fen%20is%20wearing%20a%20stage%20costume%20for%20a%20performance.%20The%20costume%20is%20a%20black%20dress%20with%20a%20cape%20and%20a%20black%20hat.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a15aa0251ede568c7e18a57%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFen%20rebuilt%20her%20career%20as%20a%20performer%20in%20Prague.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lily%20C.%20Fen%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22669b02cc-2723-448f-9059-37b30e25e34d%5C%22%3EMy%20husband%20got%20a%20job%20in%20Switzerland%2C%20and%20I%20had%20to%20reinvent%20myself%20again%E2%80%AF%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBy%202014%2C%20my%20marriage%20was%20suffering%20from%20the%20strain%20of%20unexplained%20infertility.%20As%20a%20form%20of%20%26quot%3Bmarital%20therapy%2C%26quot%3B%20we%20took%20a%20summer%20tour%2C%20spending%20several%20weeks%20in%20Norway%2C%20Switzerland%2C%20and%20Malta.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20liked%20Switzerland%20and%20applied%20for%20a%20few%20jobs%20there%20after%20we%20returned%20home.%20Before%20we%20knew%20it%2C%20he%20was%20offered%20a%20role%20at%20a%20bank%2C%20and%20we%20both%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffemale-breadwinner-moved-switzerland-job-google-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erelocated%20to%20Zurich%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222816%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Fen%20and%20her%20husband%20are%20sitting%20at%20a%20restaurant%20table%20together.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a15aa997ff506e273e67c85%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222112%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFen%20and%20her%20husband%20relocated%20from%20Prague%20to%20Switzerland%20in%202014.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lily%20C.%20Fen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20relocating%20put%20my%20husband%20and%20me%20on%20equal%20footing%2C%20both%20of%20us%20struggling%20with%20another%20language%20and%20figuring%20out%20how%20to%20make%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20many%20years%20to%20build%20connections%20as%20a%20thespian%20in%20Manila%20and%20I%20had%20to%20do%20it%20at%20turbo%20speed%20when%20I%20moved%20to%20Prague.%20Starting%20from%20scratch%20a%20third%20time%20didn't%20appeal%20to%20me%2C%20so%20I%20thought%20I'd%20revisit%20my%20love%20for%20writing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20months%20in%2C%20when%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20discovered%20that%20a%20group%20of%20migrant%20women%20wanted%20to%20build%20a%20book%20together%2C%20I%20offered%20to%20step%20in%20as%20co-editor%2C%20and%20they%20accepted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20the%20next%20decade%20building%20up%20my%20writing%20credentials%2C%20from%20travel%20articles%20to%20sharing%20my%20interests%20on%20my%20blog.%E2%80%AF%20I'm%20often%20tempted%20to%20go%20back%20to%20performing.%20I%20was%20good%20at%20it%20and%20I%20often%20miss%20it.%20But%20life%20can%20be%20unpredictable%20as%20an%20actor%2C%20and%20the%20hours%20are%20often%20unsociable.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20finally%20conceived%20in%202019%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eand%20I%20knew%20going%20from%20production%20to%20production%20wasn't%20conducive%20to%20the%20family%20life%20I%20wanted.%20Plus%2C%20I%20love%20my%20new%20identity%20as%20a%20writer%20because%20it%20helped%20me%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fupskilling-new-side-hustle-for-software-engineers-ai-era-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edevelop%20different%20skills%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20competing%20with%20my%20husband%20about%20who%20had%20a%20more%20successful%20career%20%E2%80%94%20something%20I%20unconsciously%20did%20in%20Prague%20%E2%80%94%20I've%20let%20him%20become%20our%20provider.%20He's%20established%20himself%20in%20the%20corporate%20world%2C%20while%20I%20rely%20on%20freelance%20income.%20Our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwomen-earn-vs-men-and-latest-gender-wage-gap-statistics-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewage%20gap%20%3C%2Fa%3Emakes%20me%20judge%20my%20prowess%20as%20a%20professional%20at%20times%2C%20but%20I%20insist%20on%20not%20living%20in%20that%20headspace%20and%20choose%20to%20find%20joy%20in%20earning%20a%20side%20income.%20I%20contribute%20to%20our%20household%2C%20but%20still%20have%20the%20time%20and%20flexibility%20to%20raise%20the%20child%20we%20fought%20to%20have.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22749ae238-01a1-4020-91d3-ec152d5180d4%5C%22%3EI%20don't%20regret%20choosing%20family%20over%20my%20career%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20I've%20prioritized%20my%20family%20over%20my%20profession%2C%20which%20has%20been%20very%20rewarding.%20I'm%20learning%20to%20view%20my%20husband's%20success%20as%20mine%2C%20and%20he's%20responded%20with%20the%20same%20excitement%20for%20my%20writing%20milestones%2C%20such%20as%20the%202026%20launch%20of%20my%20debut%20picture%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22893%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lily%20Fen%20is%20holding%20her%20debut%20picture%20book%20in%20her%20hands.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a15aa4151ede568c7e18a5a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221214%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFen%20holding%20her%20debut%20picture%20book.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Lily%20C.%20Fen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMoving%20to%20Prague%20and%20Zurich%20with%20my%20husband%20and%20becoming%20a%20%26quot%3Btrailing%20spouse%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20term%20I%20both%20love%20and%20hate%2C%20has%20taught%20me%20about%20letting%20go%2C%20shedding%20the%20identity%20and%20pride%20I%20had%20as%20an%20actor.%20It's%20challenged%20me%20to%20reinvent%20myself%20and%20persevere%20in%20new%20spaces.%20In%20gradually%20switching%20from%20stage%20to%20page%2C%20I've%20had%20to%20show%20up%2C%20do%20the%20work%2C%20and%20be%20ready%20for%20opportunities%20w