0contend%20with%20%26quot%3Bcritically%20low%26quot%3B%20fuel.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20Operation%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-the-us-militarys-strategic-deception-to-strike-iran-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMidnight%20Hammer%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20June%202025%2C%20US%20Air%20Force%20F-16%20fighter%20jets%20cleared%20the%20way%20for%20the%20B-2%20bombers%20that%20struck%20Iran's%20nuclear%20facilities.%20The%20fighters%20flew%20hundreds%20of%20miles%20into%20Iranian%20territory%2C%20knocked%20out%20hostile%20air%20defenses%2C%20and%20flew%20out%20with%20very%20little%20fuel%20left%20in%20the%20tank%2C%20award%20citations%20reveal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20Air%20Force%20awarded%20six%20F-16%20pilots%20from%20the%2055th%20Fighter%20Squadron%20the%20Distinguished%20Flying%20Cross%20for%20their%20part%20in%20the%20operation%2C%20with%20special%20designations%20for%20service%20in%20combat.%20The%20award%20is%20bestowed%20for%20heroism%20or%20extraordinary%20achievement%20in%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAward%20citations%20provided%20by%20the%20Air%20Force%20to%20Business%20Insider%20spotlight%20these%20aviators%2C%20who%20flew%20nearly%20300%20miles%20into%20defended%20Iranian%20airspace%20in%20non-stealth%20jets%2C%20grappled%20with%20high-risk%20fuel%20challenges%20during%20the%20mission%2C%20and%20returned%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20rare%20that%20we%20get%20a%20chance%20to%20take%20a%20peek%20into%20the%20kinds%20of%20decisions%20that%20these%20aviators%20have%20to%20make%20and%20the%20ramifications%20of%20getting%20it%20wrong%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20retired%20F-16%20pilot%20and%20former%20Navy%20TOPGUN%20instructor%20Vincent%20Aiello%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20award%20documents%20and%20the%20precarious%20situations%20the%20pilots%20faced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20operation%2C%20which%20unfolded%20nearly%20eight%20months%20before%20the%20more%20recent%20Operation%20E