%22_blank%5C%22%3EFighting%20Falcon%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20developed%20in%20the%201970s%20and%20entered%20service%20toward%20the%20end%20of%20the%20decade%2C%20while%20the%20first%20operational%20stealth%20aircraft%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-air-force-wants-help-maintaining-retired-f117-stealth-jets-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EF117%20Nighthawk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20didn't%20enter%20service%20until%20the%201980s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20operation%2C%20the%20F-16s%20%26quot%3Bemployed%20multiple%20AGM-88%20suppressive%20weapons%20against%20enemy%20threats%20protecting%20the%20bombers%20and%20their%20Airmen%20during%20their%20most%20vulnerable%20time%20over%20target%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20award%20citations%20said.%20The%20AGM-88%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-quietly-gives-ukraine-anti-radar-missiles-to-fight-russia-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHigh-speed%20Anti-Radiation%20Missiles%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20made%20to%20destroy%20radar-equipped%20air%20defense%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fighter%20pilots%20flew%20%26quot%3Bat%20grave%20risk%26quot%3B%20to%20their%20lives%20in%20the%20F-16%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20only%20aircraft%20without%20low-observable%20design%2C%20deep%20into%20a%20sophisticated%20Iranian%20integrated%20air%20and%20missile%20defense%20network%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20award%20documents%20said.%20Flying%20so%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-survival-training-that-kicks-in-after-pilot-is-down-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edeep%20into%20adversary%20territory%3C%2Fa%3E%20meant%20the%20crew%20ventured%20%26quot%3Bfar%20beyond%20the%20reach%20of%20friendly%20personnel%20recovery%20assets%26quot%3B%20and%20accepted%20%26quot%3Bthe%20considerable%20risk%20of%20capture%26quot%3B%20if%20shot%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228052c2c5-f10c-43cc-ab6f-e8b48a4ee8f2%5C%22%3EFuel%20troubles%20coming%20and%20going%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mission%20got%20off%20to%20a%20rough%20start.%20The%20pilots%2C%20including%20three%20that%20took%20off%20from%20austere%20airfields%2C%20ran%20into%20%26quot%3Bimmediate%20challenges%20upon%20initial%20take-off%20when%20alerted%20to%20air%20refueling%20fallout.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225719%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20Air%20Force%20B-2%20Spirit%20bomber%20at%20Whiteman%20Air%20Force%20Base%20in%20Missouri%2C%20before%20departing%20for%20Operation%20Midnight%20Hammer%2C%20June%202025.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a19f5ff2ab5f9757add6bcb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223813%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20Air%20Force%20B-2%20Spirit%20bomber%20at%20Whiteman%20Air%20Force%20Base%20in%20Missouri%2C%20before%20departing%20for%20Operation%20Midnight%20Hammer.%3Cp%3EUS%20Air%20Force%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFlying%20in%20and%20out%20of%20new%20and%20austere%20airfields%20is%20difficult%20even%20under%20the%20best%20of%20circumstances%2C%20Waters%20said%2C%20and%20can%20impact%20a%20pilot's%20situational%20awareness.%20Adding%20uncertainty%20about%20fuel%20only%20compounds%20the%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20award%20documents%20don't%20specify%20what%20went%20wrong%2C%20though%20two%20pilots%20were%20forced%20to%20direct%20new%20tanker%20pairings%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efor%20aircraft%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Epre-planned%20aerial%20refueling%20rendezvous%2C%20while%20others%20scrambled%20to%20rejoin%20%26quot%3Bwith%20an%20unplanned%20tanker.%26quot%3B%20These%20kinds%20of%20changes%20can%20add%20strain%20on%20the%20already%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-air-force-boom-operators-keep-calm-inherently-dangerous-job-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estressful%20aerial%20refueling%20process%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Bfuel%20fallout%26quot%3B%20cited%20in%20the%20documents%20suggests%20that%20one%20or%20more%20of%20the%20tankers%20were%20unexpectedly%20unavailable.%20For%20jet%20pilots%2C%20Waters%20said%2C%20a%20tanker%20reliability%20issue%20immediately%20becomes%20a%20fuel%20and%20timing%20problem%2C%20forcing%20rapid%2C%20complex%20decision-making.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20timeline%20delays%2C%20two%20of%20the%20F-16%20pilots%2C%20their%20citations%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bexecuted%20air%20refueling%20at%20speeds%20above%20anything%20previously%20performed%20in%20the%20F-16%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3Bensure%20acceptable%20combat%20air%20power%20force%20packaging%20into%20Iran.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20fuel%20problems%20weren't%20the%20last%20for%20the%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFighter%20jets%20rarely%20depart%20with%20maximum%20fuel%20loads%2C%20Aiello%20said.%20More%20fuel%20means%20more%20weight%2C%20which%20can%20reduce%20speed%20and%20limit%20the%20number%20of%20weapons%20that%20the%20jet%20can%20carry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20make%20it%20out%2C%20you're%20gonna%20be%20tight%20on%20gas%20to%20begin%20with%2C%26quot%3B%20Waters%20said.%20Departing%20low%20on%20fuel%20is%20common%20enough%20that%20pilots%20joke%20about%20it%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20case%2C%20the%20F-16s%20finished%20their%20escort%20mission%20%26quot%3Bcritically%20low%20on%20fuel.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20with%20fuel%20critically%20low%2C%20he%20resolutely%20escorted%20the%20package%20to%20safety%2C%20ensuring%20every%20aircraft%20made%20it%20out%20of%20harm's%20way%20before%20executing%20a%20high-stakes%20tanker%20rejoin%20while%20critically%20low%20on%20fuel%2C%26quot%3B%20reads%20the%20citation%20for%20the%20senior%20officer%2C%20Lt.%20Col.%20Christopher%20Beckett.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Air%20Force%20weapons%20specialists%20load%20missiles%20onto%20an%20F-16%20during%20a%20training%20event%20in%20Florida%2C%20April%2029%2C%202026.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a19f72c2ab5f9757add6be4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAir%20Force%20weapons%20specialists%20load%20missiles%20onto%20an%20F-16%20during%20a%20training%20event.%3Cp%3EMaster%20Sgt.%20Kregg%20York%2FUS%20Air%20National%20Guard%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20extremely%20low%20on%20fuel%2C%20Majs.%20Matthew%20Croghan%20and%20Alexander%20Trembly%20and%20Capts.%20Megan%20Langas%2C%20Abigail%20Maio%2C%20and%20Daniel%20Dodson%20each%20%26quot%3Btenaciously%20escorted%20the%20package%20to%20safety%20before%20executing%20a%20perilous%20minimum%20fuel%20tanker%20rejoin%2C%26quot%3B%20their%20citations%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a660eb54-5782-41c1-bba4-5f6f31efe24c%5C%22%3EAir%20Force%20tanker%20challenges%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20refueling%20problems%20referenced%20in%20the%20award%20citations%20point%20to%20an%20issue%20the%20Air%20Force%20is%20%26quot%3Bwhistling%20past%20the%20graveyard%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20John%20Venable%2C%20a%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20Mitchell%20Institute%20for%20Aerospace%20Studies%20and%20a%20retired%20Air%20Force%20F-16%20pilot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAircrew%20comments%20made%20during%20a%20Midnight%20Hammer%20lessons-learned%20forum%20he%20attended%20described%20tanker%20cancellations%2C%20Venable%20said%2C%20which%20forced%20major%20in-flight%20replanning%2C%20including%20changes%20to%20tanker%20tracks%20and%20receiver%20assignments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20that%20forum%2C%20Venable%20said%2C%20aviators%20recalled%20that%20on%20their%20way%20home%2C%20some%20of%20the%20jets%20hit%20their%20tankers%20%26quot%3Bon%20fumes%26quot%3B%20to%20refuel.%20Others%20could%20not%20reach%20a%20tanker%20at%20all%20and%20were%20forced%20to%20divert%20to%20some%20%26quot%3Bunusual%20locations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Air%20Force%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20Business%20Insider's%20query%20regarding%20fuel%20and%20tanker%20problems%20during%20Midnight%20Hammer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20service's%20tanker%20shortage%2C%20sometimes%20characterized%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Btanker%20gap%2C%26quot%3B%20has%20been%20exacerbated%20by%20an%20aging%20fleet%20and%20delayed%20modernization%20efforts.%20Those%20issues%20have%20been%20previously%20identified%20by%20watchdogs%2C%20congressional%20research%2C%20and%20defense%20experts%20as%20particular%20points%20of%20concern.%20There%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20backup%20capacity%2C%20even%20for%20an%20operation%20of%20limited%20scope%20and%20duration%2C%20Venable%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20tanker%20challenge%20could%20become%20far%20more%20serious%20in%20a%20Pacific%20conflict%2C%20he%20added%2C%20where%20the%20distances%20are%20significantly%20greater%20and%20aerial%20refueling%20demands%20would%20be%20much%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpilots-protected-bombers-over-iran-flew-home-on-fumes-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780133701000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a19f7de2e5a80cfe05010ff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpilots-protected-bombers-over-iran-flew-home-on-fumes-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Air%20Force%20award%20documents%20reveal%20how%20six%20F-16%20pilots%20escorted%20B-2%20bombers%20into%20Iran%2C%20for%20Midnight%20Hammer%2C%20and%20returned%20home%20nearly%20out%20of%20gas.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kbaker%40insider.com%20(Kelsey%20Baker)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Karisma%20Kapoor%E2%80%99s%20raw%20transformation%20in%20%E2%80%98Brown%E2%80%99%20trailer%20leaves%20fans%20stunned%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780133387000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131406978%2Cimgsize-37316.c