at%20investors%20need%20to%20stay%20disciplined%20to%20protect%20themselves%20from%20undue%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20short-term%20oriented%20money%20that%20is%20looking%20for%20those%20next%20moves%20and%20is%20treating%20stocks%20to%20some%20degree%20like%20lottery%20tickets%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20strategist%20said%2C%20explaining%20that%20recent%20upward%20swings%20in%20the%20market%20could%20lead%20to%20higher%20concentration%20risk.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESonders%20said%20it's%20time%20for%20investors%20employ%20a%20rebalancing%20strategy%20to%20make%20sure%20their%20portfolio%20isn't%20overly%20concentrated%20on%20any%20particular%20part%20of%20the%20market%2C%20especially%20during%20a%20time%20when%20speculative%20momentum%20is%20in%20the%20drivers%20seat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHeed%20the%20old%20line%20of%2C%20'no%20one%20ever%20went%20broke%20taking%20profits%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20%26quot%3BI%20understand%20the%20desire%20to%20let%20winners%20run%2C%20but%20I%20do%20think%20that%20a%20rebalancing%20strategy%20is%20the%20best%20way%20to%20think%20about%20reigning%20in%20some%20of%20where%20that%20speculative%20excess%20might%20cause%20some%20concentration%20problem%20in%20your%20own%20portfolios.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-record-high-rally-investing-strategy-wall-street-stocks-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780132801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a19d0542ab5f9757add68cc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-record-high-rally-investing-strategy-wall-street-stocks-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20stock%20market%20notched%20another%20winning%20week%2C%20but%20one%20Wall%20Street%20pro%20warns%20that%20investors%20are%20exhibiting%20some%20%26quot%3Bcasino-lik