on's%20artistry%20on%20musicians%20worldwide%2C%20including%20India's%20most%20revered%20voice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20class%20of%202026%20might%20have%20to%20pivot%20in%20their%20job%20hunt%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227303%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Students%20wearing%20blue%20caps%20and%20gowns%20at%20a%20graduation%20ceremony%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a19a0f62e5a80cfe050093f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225477%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECollege%20grads%20might%20need%20to%20pivot%20in%20their%20job%20search%2C%20such%20as%20searching%20for%20internships%20instead%20of%20full-time%20work.%3Cp%3Eferrantraite%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESome%20fields%20that%20tend%20to%20attract%20college%20grads%20may%20be%20difficult%20to%20enter%20quickly.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENew%20job%20seekers%20having%20a%20hard%20time%20landing%20work%20can%20make%20some%20pivots.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20grad%20focusing%20on%20applying%20to%20big%20companies%20can%20switch%20their%20strategy%20to%20small%20businesses.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Cross%20Sierra%2C%20the%20path%20from%20college%20to%20career%20has%20included%20an%20accelerated%20MBA%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-hired-job-search-white-collar-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enationwide%20job%20search%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20crashing%20on%20friends'%20couches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2023-year-old%20hopes%20to%20become%20a%20high%20school%20athletic%20director.%20So%20far%2C%20though%2C%20he's%20only%20become%20frustrated%20by%20what%20feels%20like%20an%20impossible%20job%20market%20to%20break%20into.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20more%20do%20I%20have%20to%20do%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEconomists%20and%20workplace%20observers%20say%20it's%20a%20question%20many%20recent%20graduates%20are%20asking.%20Despite%20the%20usual%20advice%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetworking-important-new-job-economy-ai-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimportance%20of%20networking%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20conducting%20a%20targeted%20job%20search%2C%20the%20market%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-changing-entry-level-work-advice-to-succeed-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eentry-level%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20tougher%20than%20it%20was%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHiring%20has%20slowed%20across%20much%20of%20the%20economy%2C%20leaving%20fewer%20openings%20and%20longer%20searches%20for%20many%20newcomers.%20In%20fields%20that%20tend%20to%20draw%20fresh%20grads%20%E2%80%94%20including%20finance%2C%20professional%20and%20business%20services%2C%20and%20healthcare%20%E2%80%94%20hiring%20rates%20are%20about%20as%20low%20as%20they've%20been%20since%20the%20pandemic%2C%20said%20Dante%20DeAntonio%2C%20senior%20director%20of%20economic%20research%20at%20Moody's%20Analytics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJob%20seekers%20might%20need%20to%20consider%20pivoting%20their%20approach.%20If%20you're%20applying%20only%20to%20big-name%20companies%2C%20you%20could%20widen%20your%20search%20to%20include%20smaller%20employers.%20If%20you're%20an%20accounting%20major%20focused%20on%20landing%20a%20job%20at%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-four-pwc-cuts-offices-offer-entry-level-consulting-jobs-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBig%20Four%20firm%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you%20might%20also%20look%20at%20accounting%20roles%20in%20other%20industries.%20And%20if%20you're%20set%20on%20a%20full-time%20job%2C%20you%20may%20need%20to%20consider%20an%20internship%20as%20a%20way%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFocus%20on%20getting%20your%20foot%20in%20the%20door%2C%20even%20if%20it's%20not%20the%20ideal%20thing%20you%20want%2C%26quot%3B%20economist%20Guy%20Berger%20said.%20%26quot%3BOnce%20you%20have%20a%20job%2C%20it%20becomes%20much%20less%20stressful%20to%20look%20for%20another%20one.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBerger%20said%20both%20high%20school%20and%20college%20graduates%20should%20expect%20a%20longer%20job%20search%20and%20be%20flexible%20with%20offers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20underemployment%20rate%20for%20recent%20college%20graduates%20has%20edged%20down%20from%20its%202025%20high%20of%2042.4%25%2C%20but%20at%2041.5%25%20in%20March%2C%20it%20is%20still%20above%20its%20late%202024%20low.%20That%20data%2C%20published%20by%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20New%20York%2C%20suggests%20some%20graduates%20are%20taking%20positions%20that%20don't%20require%20their%20years%20of%20schooling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FrpwVT%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Line%20chart%20of%20the%20underemployment%20rates%20of%20recent%20college%20graduates%20since%202019%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2FrpwVT%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20hot%20post-pandemic%20labor%20market%20of%202022%2C%20job%20hunters%20could%20be%20picky%2C%20Berger%20said.%20If%20they%20didn't%20like%20something%2C%20it%20was%20easy%20to%20move%20on.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20it's%20the%20kind%20of%20thing%20where%20you%20might%20have%20to%20bide%20your%20time%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2202c4871f-fea0-4c16-9b88-e68245e0ad49%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECollege%20graduates%20are%20going%20to%20have%20to%20be%20flexible%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20difficulty%20of%20finding%20work%20can%20depend%20on%20where%20you%20are%20hoping%20to%20end%20up.%20Cory%20Stahle%2C%20senior%20economist%20at%20the%20job%20platform%20Indeed%2C%20said%20healthcare%20and%20education%20jobs%20have%20clear%20pathways%20that%20could%20make%20the%20job%20search%20less%20onerous.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20going%20to%20have%20an%20easier%20time%20finding%20a%20job%20versus%20something%20that's%20more%20kind%20of%20market-based%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20grads%20looking%20for%20work%20in%20those%20fields.%20Healthcare%2C%20in%20general%2C%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-aging-ai-reshaping-job-market-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epropping%20up%20the%20job%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20and%20helped%20keep%20overall%20job%20growth%20positive%20in%202025%20as%20hiring%20has%20lagged%20in%20other%20industries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20possible%20hiccup%20for%20new%20grads%3A%20AI.%20Some%20large%20companies%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecent-company-layoffs-laying-off-workers-2026%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaying%20off%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20investing%20in%20technology.%20That%20search%20for%20efficiency%20will%20push%20some%20employers%20to%20cut%20back%20on%20hiring%20less-experienced%20workers%20in%20hopes%20that%20AI%20could%20take%20on%20some%20of%20the%20load%2C%20DeAntonio%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20domino%20to%20fall%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20pullback%20in%20hiring%20amongst%20younger%20workers%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnxiety%20about%20AI%20and%20its%20effect%20on%20work%20is%20spilling%20into%20graduation%20ceremonies%2C%20where%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudents-boo-eric-schmidt-google-ceo-ai-university-arizona-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudents%20have%20booed%20speakers%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20mention%20the%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPriya%20Rathod%2C%20workplace%20trends%20editor%20at%20Indeed%2C%20said%20grads%20might%20have%20to%20take%20a%20less%20direct%20route%20into%20their%20careers%20than%20they%20did%20a%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20though%20that%20doesn't%20make%20those%20paths%20any%20less%20promising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20career%20is%20going%20to%20be%20more%20like%20a%20lattice%20than%20a%20ladder%2C%20so%20remember%20that%20even%20if%20you%20don't%20have%20the%20perfect%20role%20right%20now%2C%20it%20doesn't%20inhibit%20you%20from%20getting%20that%20perfect%20role%20down%20the%20road%2C%26quot%3B%20Rathod%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGraduates%20might%20need%20to%20rethink%20what%20a%20first%20step%20looks%20like.%20Contract%20work%2C%20temporary%20jobs%2C%20and%20internships%20can%20help%20build%20experience%20while%20the%20search%20for%20a%20permanent%20role%20continues.%20Postings%20on%20Indeed%20through%20April%20suggest%20demand%20for%20interns%20has%20been%20pretty%20strong%2C%20roughly%20in%20line%20with%202024%20levels%20and%20above%202025.%20While%20some%20internships%20are%20limited%20to%20enrolled%20students%2C%20the%20positions%20can%20lead%20to%20full-time%20offers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20help%20you%20understand%20how%20the%20company%20functions%2C%26quot%3B%20Rathod%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20going%20to%20help%20you%20make%20connections%20within%20the%20company.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2F18SDd%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22feedlyNoScript%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Line%20chart%20with%20three%20lines%20that%20shows%20indexed%20internship%20postings%20on%20Indeed%20since%202024%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2F18SDd%2Ffull.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3ERathod%20also%20pointed%20to%20the%20National%20Federation%20of%20Independent%20Business's%20jobs%20report%2C%20which%20showed%20that%20about%20a%20third%20of%20small%20business%20owners%20had%20openings%20they%20couldn't%20fill%20%E2%80%94%20the%20highest%20level%20since%20June%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20smaller%20employers%20can%20offer%20graduates%20a%20wider%20range%20of%20experiences%20and%20greater%20opportunities%20to%20build%20relationships%20with%20senior%20colleagues%20who%20could%20become%20mentors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20can%20help%20give%20you%20access%20to%20things%20that%20you%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20engage%20in%20or%20projects%20you%20wouldn't%20be%20able%20to%20engage%20in%20at%20larger%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20Rathod%20said%20of%20smaller%20firms.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224b6e1cc2-786f-48c6-8c67-45a88d603302%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPeople%20can%20also%20pivot%20how%20they%20job%20search%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20only%20looking%20at%20job%20boards%2C%20take%20the%20hunt%20to%20social%20media.%20Anya%20Roodnitsky%2C%20who%20attended%20Dartmouth%20College%2C%20landed%20a%20job%20after%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollege-student-made-hire-me-video-led-to-job-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evideo%20on%20Instagram%20went%20viral%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20leading%20to%20coffee%20chats%20and%20new%20connections.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20sitting%20in%20the%20kitchen%2C%20and%20had%20just%20hit%20'submit'%20on%20my%20300th%20application.%20I%20was%20like%2C%20'This%20isn't%20working%2C'%26quot%3B%20Roodnitsky%20said%20in%20an%20as-told-to%20essay%20with%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt%20hit%20me%20that%20I%20should%20create%20a%20funny%20presentation%20video.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESomeone%20who%20saw%20her%20video%20flagged%20a%20job%20posting%20at%20an%20energy%20company.%20%26quot%3BI%20applied%2C%20and%20the%20company's%20recruiter%20reached%20out%20the%20next%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Roodnitsky%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Sierra%2C%20who%20completed%20his%20MBA%20in%20May%20at%20a%20college%20in%20New%20Hampshire%2C%20the%20plan%20is%20to%20stay%20with%20a%20friend%20and%20spend%20the%20summer%20coaching%20for%20a%20travel%20baseball%20club%20in%20Massachusetts.%20If%20that%20doesn't%20turn%20into%20a%20full-time%20gig%2C%20he'll%20continue%20searching%20%E2%80%94%20as%20he%20has%20for%20more%20than%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20just%20got%20to%20keep%20my%20head%20down%20and%20keep%20going%2C%26quot%3B%20Sierra%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20too%20will%20end.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollege-grads-class-of-2026-job-searching-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780130941000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a199d4cb4fb977f35981834%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcollege-grads-class-of-2026-job-searching-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Finding%20a%20job%20could%20be%20tough%20for%20new%20college%20grads.%20Those%20looking%20for%20full-time%20work%20may%20have%20to%20pivot%20to%20internships%20or%20make%20other%20changes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Madison%20Hoff%2CTim%20Paradis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20The%20War%20Rages%20In%20Iran%2C%20Tensions%20Brew%20In%20Another%20Part%20Of%20The%20World%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22North%20Korea's%20nuclear%20defiance%2C%20a%20drone%20strike%20in%20Romania%2C%20China's%20silo%20expansion%20and%20Kazakhstan's%20offer%20to%20store%20Tehran's%20uranium%20stockpile%20present%20themselves%20as%20multiple%20flashpoints.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780130885000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2026-05%2Ffcimm0d_romania-drone-strike_625x300_30_May_26.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fbeyon