st-Operation%20Sindoor%2C%20shifting%20towards%20preemptive%2C%20technology-driven%20deterrence.%20New%20formations%20like%20Rudra%20Brigades%20and%20Bhairav%20battalions%2C%20alongside%20integrated%20drone%20units%2C%20are%20enhancing%20combat%20readiness.%20This%20modernization%20focuses%20on%20unmanned%20systems%2C%20AI%2C%20and%20rapid%20response%2C%20reflecting%20a%20decisive%20move%20from%20manpower-heavy%20tactics%20to%20a%20high-tech%2C%20multi-domain%20force.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20NEWS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A99%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%20AI%20CEO%20explains%20how%20much%20he%20spent%20on%20Codex%20last%20month%20%E2%80%94%20and%20why%20he's%20still%20'very%20nice'%20when%20prompting%20the%20tech%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227578%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dan%20Shipper%2C%20dressed%20in%20a%20blue%20jean%20button-down%2C%20talks%20onstage.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a173fd52ab5f9757add50c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225282%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDan%20Shipper%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20media%20and%20AI%20software%20company%20Every%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20he%20thinks%20people%20are%20underestimating%20Codex.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Broadway%2FSportsfile%20for%20Web%20Summit%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDan%20Shipper%20says%20his%20AI-focused%20company%20%E2%80%94%20Every%20%E2%80%94%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20on%20his%20token%20use.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAI%20reads%20and%20drafts%20his%20emails%2C%20he%20said.%20It's%20also%20helping%20the%20company%20create%20pitch%20decks.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20Every%20believes%20it's%20building%20an%20employee%20model%20that%20looks%20like%20the%20future%20of%20business.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartups-are-flinging-job-offers-at-dan-shipper-but-the-20-year-old-philosphy-major-rould-rather-stay-at-upenn-2012-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDan%20Shipper%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20he%20doesn't%20write%20many%20of%20his%20routine%20emails.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Every%20%E2%80%94%20an%20AI-focused%20media%2C%20software%2C%20and%20consulting%20company%20%E2%80%94%20said%20he%20uses%20OpenAI's%20Codex%20to%20read%20his%20inbox%2C%20check%20his%20calendar%2C%20propose%20meeting%20times%2C%20and%20draft%20responses.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tool%20is%20not%20allowed%20to%20send%20emails%20without%20his%20approval%2C%20but%20Shipper%20said%20much%20of%20the%20scheduling%20correspondence%20around%20his%20Business%20Insider%20interview%20was%20generated%20by%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20the%20words%20are%20pretty%20much%20Codex%2C%26quot%3B%20Shipper%20said.%20He's%20considering%20changing%20the%20%26quot%3BFrom%3A%26quot%3B%20field%20in%20his%20email%20to%20indicate%20when%20messages%20are%20drafted%20with%20his%20AI%20agent's%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20New%20York%20City-based%20business%20is%20built%20around%20AI.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthese-kids-became-stars-in-tech-before-they-turned-20-2012-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EShipper%20cofounded%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20company%20in%202020%20with%20backing%20from%20Starting%20Line%20and%20Reid%20Hoffman.%20It%20writes%20its%20own%20technology%20newsletter%2C%20sells%20AI%20consulting%20and%20training%20services%2C%20and%20builds%20apps%20like%20Sparkle%2C%20a%20computer-file%20automation%20tool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20also%20gets%20early%20access%20to%20models%20and%20tools%20from%20major%20AI%20companies%2C%20including%20OpenAI%20and%20Anthropic%2C%20giving%20Shipper%20a%20close-up%20view%20of%20where%20the%20tech%20is%20heading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20perspective%20has%20made%20him%20optimistic%20about%20how%20people%20will%20work%20in%20the%20future.%20And%20he%20thinks%20his%20business%20is%20structured%20like%20a%20company%20of%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20optimism%20is%20expensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f7e7f7eb-3e24-4ab7-bd34-58162378d057%5C%22%3EEvery's%20AI%20expenses%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.x.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EExtremely%20smart%20take%20on%20the%20tokenmaxxing%20panic%20and%20why%20it%20won%E2%80%99t%20last%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FSu1yOhAuL7%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FSu1yOhAuL7%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Dan%20Shipper%20%F0%9F%93%A7%20(%40danshipper)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fdanshipper%2Fstatus%2F2060382815821209801%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2029%2C%202026%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EShipper%20told%20Business%20Insider%20he%20spent%20about%20%2413%2C000%20on%20his%20personal%20Codex%20overages%20last%20month%2C%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20AI%20bills%20he%20could%20recall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20got%20some%20side%20eye%20from%20our%20COO%2C%20Brandon%20Gell%2C%20on%20that%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsked%20how%20much%20larger%20that%20bill%20was%20compared%20with%20the%20same%20month%20last%20year%2C%20Shipper%20responded%3A%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EWay%20%3C%2Fem%3Emore.%20Way%2C%20way%2C%20way%2C%20way%2C%20way%2C%20way%2C%20way%2C%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Every%2C%20AI%20access%20is%20just%20part%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20employing%20people.%20All%2027%20full-time%20employees%20get%20the%20entry-level%20%2420-a-month%20subscriptions%2C%20while%20technical%20workers%20get%20%24200-a-month%20plans%2C%20and%20the%20company%20pays%20overages.%20Token%20budgets%20are%20akin%20to%20other%20employee%20costs%2C%20like%20health%20insurance%20or%20company-issued%20laptops%2C%20Shipper%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20the%20high%20costs%2C%20nobody%20at%20Every%20has%20been%20told%20they're%20spending%20too%20much%20on%20tokens%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20started%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20we%20will%20think%20about%20overages%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAs%20long%20as%20you%20don't%20spend%20so%20much%20money%20that%20we%20go%20bankrupt%2C%20we'll%20be%20fine.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f6415b81-7ded-46d8-8c53-57097540704d%5C%22%3EAI%20changed%20how%20the%20company%20works%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEvery's%20spending%20shows%20how%20deeply%20embedded%20AI%20has%20become%20in%20its%20workflow.%20Shipper%20said%20the%20company%20once%20experimented%20with%20giving%20every%20employee%20their%20own%20AI%20agent%2C%20but%20moved%20away%20from%20that%20model%20because%20the%20agents%20required%20too%20much%20upkeep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20Every%20now%20uses%20a%20smaller%20number%20of%20agents%20that%20serve%20specific%20teams%20or%20the%20whole%20company.%20One%20of%20them%2C%20called%20Claudie%2C%20helps%20the%20consulting%20team%20draft%20initial%20slide%20decks%2C%20put%20together%20sales%20proposals%2C%20and%20track%20client%20to-dos%20by%20reading%20transcripts%20and%20updating%20the%20company's%20task%20manager.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShipper%20said%20he%20does%20not%20see%20those%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-changing-entry-level-work-advice-to-succeed-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etools%20as%20replacing%20Every's%20workers%3C%2Fa%3E%20outright.%20Instead%2C%20he%20said%20that%20AI%20could%20push%20more%20people%20into%20manager-like%20roles%20earlier%20in%20their%20careers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVery%20few%20people%20actually%20get%20the%20opportunity%20to%20be%20managers%2C%20because%20managing%20humans%20is%20very%20expensive%20and%20risky%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20many%2C%20many%20more%20people%20are%20capable%20of%20that%20than%20we%20think.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Shipper%20said%20AI%20has%20limits.%20As%20a%20writer%2C%20he%20said%2C%20the%20technology%20is%20useful%20for%20research%2C%20drafting%2C%20and%20editing%2C%20but%20it%20is%20not%20especially%20good%20at%20knowing%20what%20is%20interesting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20where%20he%20thinks%20humans%20still%20matter%20most%3A%20not%20in%20doing%20every%20task%20by%20hand%2C%20but%20in%20knowing%20what%20is%20worth%20doing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221a14ad4a-8fcb-4c67-a18f-dce601097187%5C%22%3EPredictions%20for%20AI's%20future%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224471%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22sam%20altman%20onstage%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%20March%202026%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69bd795058b5806618e7cce2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222982%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EShipper%20thinks%20OpenAI%20%2C%20and%20its%20CEO%20Sam%20Altman%2C%20might%20have%20a%20trick%20up%20its%20sleeve.%3Cp%3EAnna%20Moneymaker%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20Anthropic%20is%20all%20the%20rage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20startup%20just%20launched%20its%20well-received%20update%20to%20its%20Opus%20model%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-surpasses-openai-with-965b-valuation-debuts-opus-4-8-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eleapfrogged%20OpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20the%20nation's%20most%20valuable%20AI%20company%2C%20and%20is%20racing%20toward%20its%20IPO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShipper%20is%20betting%20that%20OpenAI's%20Codex%20is%20better%20positioned%20than%20many%20people%20realize.%20He%20said%20Anthropic%20has%20%26quot%3Ba%20ton%20of%20momentum%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20predicted%20the%20narrative%20around%20OpenAI%20could%20shift%20over%20the%20next%20few%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20they're%20doing%20with%20Codex%20is%20incredibly%20impressive%2C%26quot%3B%20h