d%20neck%20lines%20visible.%20Concept%20of%20skincare%20routine%2C%20self-care%2C%20beauty%2C%20anti-aging%20prevention%20and%20healthy%20skin%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a19a7942ab5f9757add64c9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224672%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPeople%20in%20their%2020s%20and%2030s%20are%20spending%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%20to%20treat%20or%20prevent%20%26quot%3Btech%20neck.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EMarina%20Demeshko%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAre%20you%20getting%20a%20prematurely%20wrinkled%2C%20creased%20neck%20from%20spending%20hours%20on%20your%20laptop%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIf%20so%2C%20you%20just%20might%20have%20'tech%20neck.'%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPeople%20are%20spending%20big%20money%20on%20creams%2C%20gadgets%2C%20and%20procedures%20to%20try%20to%20prevent%20or%20reverse%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENora%20Ephron%20was%20around%2062%20when%2C%20in%202003%2C%20she%20wrote%20that%20she%20felt%20bad%20about%20her%20aging%20neck.%20Today%2C%20a%20distinctly%20modern%20phenomenon%20known%20as%20%26quot%3Btech%20neck%26quot%3B%20is%20leaving%20people%20as%20young%20as%20their%20early%2020s%20feeling%20the%20same%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20not%20an%20official%20diagnosis%2C%20the%20term%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-tech-neck-neck-pain-from-phone-2017-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etech%20neck%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20is%20popular%20on%20social%20media%20and%20recognized%20by%20dermatologists%2C%20plastic%20surgeons%2C%20and%20physical%20therapists.%20It%20refers%20to%20horizontal%20lines%20or%20creases%20on%20the%20neck%2C%20as%20well%20as%20postural%20changes%20such%20as%20rounded%20shoulders%20and%20a%20forward%20head%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnyone%20can%20get%20tech%20neck%2C%20but%20based%20on%20social%20media%20posts%2C%20women%20in%20their%2020s%20and%2030s%20are%20most%20concerned%20about%20preventing%20or%20%26quot%3Bfixing%26quot%3B%20its%20signs%2C%20with%20some%20spending%20upward%20of%20%245%2C000%20to%20reduce%20fine%20lines%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fimproving-posture-aging-longevity-trend-facelift-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eimprove%20posture%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELindsey%20Wallace%2C%20a%2035-year-old%20marketing%20director%20based%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20first%20learned%20about%20tech%20neck%20from%20an%20Instagram%20reel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20became%20my%20latest%20fixation%20when%20I%20looked%20in%20the%20mirror%2C%20and%20I%20noted%20lines%20getting%20deeper.%20My%20neck%20and%20upper%20chest%20was%20changing%20at%20a%20rate%20that%20my%20face%20wasn't%2C%26quot%3B%20Wallace%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BAs%20soon%20as%20I%20turned%2030%2C%20I%20would%20say%20is%20when%20I%20became%20concerned%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20quite%20know%20the%20term%20yet%2C%20or%20why%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fskincare-habits-that-lead-to-faster-wrinkles-aging-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrinkles%20were%20appearing%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20it%20all%20makes%20sense%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BI%20am%20hunched%20over%20a%20computer%20for%20over%2010%20hours%20a%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bdd4ba13-dfb3-440e-b76f-198b3441deef%5C%22%3E%245%2C000%20for%20a%20fresher%20neck%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDr.%20Kristy%20Hamilton%2C%20a%20board-certified%20plastic%20surgeon%20based%20in%20Houston%2C%20Texas%2C%20and%20social%20media%20chair%20of%20the%20American%20Society%20of%20Plastic%20Surgeons%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20tech%20neck%20is%20%26quot%3Bboth%20a%20musculoskeletal%20and%20aesthetic%20concern.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20a%20person%20hunches%20over%20a%20laptop%2C%20tablet%2C%20or%20phone%20for%20a%20lengthy%20period%20of%20time%2C%20the%20head%20tilts%20forward%20and%20places%20significant%20stress%20on%20the%20cervical%20spine%20and%20surrounding%20tissues%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20The%20delicate%2C%20thinner%20skin%20of%20the%20neck%20ages%20faster%20than%20the%20face%20because%20we%20constantly%20move%20it%20in%20different%20directions%2C%20which%20leads%20to%20creases.%20A%20consistent%20downward-facing%20posture%20speeds%20up%20this%20process%20as%20the%20skin%20is%20repeatedly%20folded%2C%20Hamilton%20said%2C%20and%20weakens%20the%20supportive%20muscles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20short%20term%2C%20patients%20may%20notice%20stiffness%20and%20soreness.%20But%20over%20time%2C%20untreated%20tech%20neck%20can%20contribute%20to%20spinal%20misalignment%20and%20chronic%20pain%2C%20as%20well%20as%20accelerated%20skin%20aging%2C%20Hamilton%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Wallace%2C%20it's%20the%20aesthetics%20that%20bother%20her%20%E2%80%94%20a%20lot.%20So%20much%20so%20that%20she%20estimates%20she's%20spent%20at%20least%20%245%2C000%20trying%20to%20correct%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20night%2C%20she%20uses%20a%20neck%20firming%20cream%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fbeauty%2Fbest-red-light-therapy-mask%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ered%20light%20therapy%20mask%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20hydrating%20collagen%20neck%20mask%2C%20and%20a%20high%20frequency%20wand%2C%20a%20handheld%20device%20that%20stimulates%20the%20skin%20with%20electric%20current%20and%20neon%20gas%2C%20from%20the%20skincare%20brand%20NuDerma.%20On%20top%20of%20that%2C%20every%20six%20months%2C%20she%20gets%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-go-to-med-spas-abroad-save-money-treatments-injectables-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elaser%20treatment%3C%2Fa%3E%20called%20CoolPeel%2C%20which%20stimulates%20collagen%20production%20by%20creating%20microinjuries%20in%20the%20skin%2C%20and%20costs%20about%20%241%2C200%20to%20%241%2C600%20per%20session%20for%20the%20face%20and%20neck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20skincare%20products%20leave%20her%20neck%20feeling%20smoother%20and%20more%20hydrated%20when%20she's%20consistent%2C%20but%20she%20believes%20the%20laser%20treatment%20has%20had%20the%20biggest%20impact%20on%20reversing%20her%20fine%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELauren%20Cummings%2C%20a%2031-year-old%20PR%20account%20executive%20based%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20has%20spent%20around%20%241%2C000%20on%20tech%20neck%20treatments%20since%20she%20became%20concerned%20about%20postural%20issues%20and%20some%20horizontal%20lines%20on%20her%20neck%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%20She's%20paid%20for%20chiropractor%20appointments%2C%20tightening%20creams%2C%20and%20done%20one%20session%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpharmacist-does-one-science-backed-tweakment-microneedling-what-is-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecollagen-stimulating%20laser%20treatmen%3C%2Fa%3Et%20called%20EVERESSE.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20getting%20more%20concerned%20as%20I'm%20now%20in%20my%2030's%20and%20want%20to%20prevent%20it%20from%20getting%20worse%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20James%20Sheridan%2C%20a%2038-year-old%20engineering%20and%20product%20development%20firm%20CEO%20who%20has%20spent%20hundreds%20reversing%20his%20tech%20neck%2C%20the%20condition%20reflects%20a%20wider%20problem%20with%20modern%20working%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20conversations%20are%20usually%20less%20about%20vanity%20and%20more%20about%20how%20modern%20work%20slowly%20wears%20on%20your%20neck%2C%20back%2C%20wrists%2C%20and%20eyes%20if%20you're%20not%20careful%2C%26quot%3B%20Sheridan%2C%20who%20is%20based%20in%20Vancouver%2C%20Washington%2C%20said%20of%20discussions%20he%20has%20with%20friends%20about%20the%20neck.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228607cc49-4e72-4f2e-a694-531b7e638dc9%5C%22%3ENeck-maxxing%20now%20to%20prevent%20tech%20neck%20later%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20of%20those%20on%20the%20tech-neck%20lookout%2C%20the%20battle%20starts%20early.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChloe%20Coles%2C%20a%2024-year-old%20health%20and%20wellness%20PR%20account%20executive%20at%20Everything%20Branding%20based%20in%20San%20Diego%2C%20said%20tech%20neck%20is%20a%20regular%20topic%20of%20conversation%20among%20the%20women%20in%20their%2020s%20at%20her%20office.%20She%2C%20for%20one%2C%20doesn't%20have%20it%20yet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'd%20say%20I'm%20more%20concerned%20that%20it%20could%20become%20a%20problem%2C%20so%20I%20try%20to%20stay%20on%20top%20of%20it%20before%20it%20gets%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Coles%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223837%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20headshot%20of%20a%20young%20woman.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a19a7f3b4fb977f3598195f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222878%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChloe%20Coles%2C%2024%2C%20has%20spent%20a%20few%20hundred%20dollars%20in%20the%20hopes%20of%20preventing%20tech%20neck.%3Cp%3EEverything%20Branding%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20her%20team%20keeps%20their%20screens%20at%20eye%20level%20to%20avoid%20slouching%2C%20uses%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-standing-desk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estanding%20desk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20takes%20advantage%20of%20the%20communal%20wearable%20red%20light%20therapy%20device.%20Caroline%20Applegate%2C%2024%2C%20also%20an%20account%20executive%20at%20the%20agency%2C%20said%20she%20bought%20a%20%24134.99%20side-sleeper%20pillow%20to%20support%20her%20posture%20while%20she%20sleeps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20use%20computer%20holders%20for%20better%20posture%2C%20do%20some%20workouts%20to%20make%20sure%20we%20are%20sitting%20up%20right%20and%20not%20looking%20down%2C%20have%20pillows%20on%20our%20chairs%20that%20also%20help%20with%20posture%2C%26quot%3B%20Coles%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224896%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20group%20of%20women%20pose%20with%20an%20LED%20device.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a198d1c2e5a80cfe0500800%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223672%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Everything%20Branding%20team%20with%20their%20office%20red%20light%20therapy%20device.%3Cp%3EChloe%20Coles%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EColes%20estimates%20she's%20spent%20a%20few%20hundred%20dollars%20on%20neck%20skincare%2C%20weight%20training%2C%20yoga%2C%20Pilates%2C%20and%20Thai%20massages%20to%20actively%20combat%20tech%20neck.%20She%20thinks%20that%20the%20combination%20of%20everything%20she's%20tried%20%26quot%3Bseems%20to%20make%20a%20difference.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYahya%20Khan%2C%20a%2029-year-old%20founder%20based%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20noticed%20lines%20on%20his%20neck%20two%20years%20ago%2C%20and%20they've%20affected%20his%20mood%20at%20work%20more%20than%20he%20expected.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%20running%20a%20business%2C%20and%20your%20appearance%20is%20part%20of%20how%20clients%20perceive%20your%20credibility%2C%20you%20notice%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Khan%20has%20spent%20about%20%24400%20so%20far%20trying%20to%20fix%20his%20fine%20lines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20stands%20in%20front%20of%20a%20yacht.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a198e7b2e5a80cfe0500811%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EYahya%20Khan%20worries%20about%20that%20tech%20neck%20could%20affect%20his%20career.%3Cp%3EYahya%20Khan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2231b5dbf6-092a-48bc-8629-7cf6cdeeebc2%5C%22%3EAll%20aboard%20the%20tech-neck%20prevention%20train%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAnti-aging%20neck%20creams%20have%20been%20around%20for%20decades%2C%20but%20the%20rise%20of%20tech%20neck%20has%20given%20skincare%20brands%20an%20opportunity%20to%20market%20them%20to%20a%20younger%20crowd.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUlta%2C%20the%20beauty%20retailer%20particularly%20popular%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.similarweb.com%2Fwebsite%2Fulta.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epeople%20aged%2025%20to%2030%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20launched%20six%20new%20neck-focused%20skin%20products%20between%202025%20and%202026.%20There%20are%2064%20neck-focused%20products%20available%20on%20Ulta's%20website%20and%2014%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fulta-beauty-ceo-kecia-steelman-glp1-craze-haircare-skincare-products-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESephora's%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20February%2C%20SickScience's%20ShapeShift%20Advanced%20Jaw%20%26amp%3B%20Neck%20Firming%20Serum%2C%20a%20product%20that%20claims%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bclinically%20shown%20to%20reduce%20the%20appearance%20of%20skin%20slackening%2C%20crepiness%2C%20and%20tech%20neck%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20added%20to%20the%20Ulta%20stocklist.%20K-beauty%20brand%20Anua's%20Collagen%20Retinol%20Refining%20Gua%20Sha%20Cream%2C%20launched%20in%20March%20and%20currently%20sold%20exclusively%20at%20Ulta%2C%20promises%20to%20help%20address%20%26quot%3Btech%20neck%20concerns%20with%20consistent%20use.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20products%20add%20to%20the%20bevy%20of%20goods%20and%20services%20showing%20up%20on%20the%20market%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsilicon-valley-biohacking-wellness-event-best-hacks-not-what-expected-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehealth%20optimization%20trends%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20biohacking%20and%20looksmaxxing%20take%20hold%20with%20consumers.%20Tech%20neck%20creams%20and%20gadgets%20are%20by%20no%20means%20the%20only%20products%20people%20are%20shelling%20out%20on%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fhot-at-work%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ekeep%20looking%20good%20in%20the%20workplace%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20people%20are%20dishing%20out%20thousands%20for%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3