a%20record%20142%2C000%20high-net-worth%20individuals%20%E2%80%94%20defined%20as%20people%20with%20over%20%241%20million%20in%20liquid%20assets%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-country-richest-people-moving-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emigrated%20to%20new%20countries%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20private%20wealth%20research%20firm%20Henley%20%26amp%3B%20Partners.%20That%20number%20is%20expected%20to%20balloon%20past%20165%2C000%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20migration%20is%20only%20part%20of%20the%20story.%20For%20the%20richest%20families%2C%20the%20bigger%20play%20is%20optionality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGarcia%20said%20taxes%20are%20a%20major%20motivator.%20In%20California%2C%20where%20many%20of%20America's%20richest%20people%20built%20their%20companies%2C%20legislators%20are%20considering%20a%20ballot%20proposal%20that%20could%20impose%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcalifornia-billionaires-list-wealth-tax-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eone-time%205%25%20tax%20on%20the%20net%20worth%20of%20billionaires%3C%2Fa%3E%20residing%20in%20the%20state.%20New%20York%20City%20just%20passed%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgov-kathy-hochul-zohran-mamdani-tax-billionaires-nyc-second-homes-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epied-%C3%A0-terre%20tax%3C%2Fa%3E%20aimed%20at%20high-end%20secondary%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20darker%2C%20maybe%20chimerical%20concerns%20about%20political%20realignments%20and%20existential%20global%20threats%2C%20from%20artificial%20intelligence%20going%20sideways%20to%20nuclear%20escalation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20sounds%20melodramatic%20until%20you've%20sat%20through%20the%20off%E2%80%91the%E2%80%91record%20dinner%20conversations%2C%26quot%3B%20Garcia%20said.%20%26quot%3BFor%20that%20crowd%2C%20the%20Southern%20Cone%20looks%20like%20a%20literal%20and%20figurative%20safe%20distance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Argentina%20is%20an%20unusual%20hedge%2C%20Garcia%20said.%20The%20country%20has%20a%20long%20history%20of%20inflation%2C%20currency%20crises%2C%20capital%20controls%2C%20and%20abrupt%20legal%20changes%20%E2%80%94%20exactly%20the%20sort%20of%20instability%20wealthy%20families%20typically%20hate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20tension%20may%20be%20the%20point.%20Argentina%20does%20not%20have%20to%20become%20the%20next%20Miami%20to%20matter.%20For%20the%20billionaire%20class%2C%20it's%20another%20door%20they%20can%20keep%20open.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Thiel%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeter-thiel-argentina-billionaire-moving-abroad-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780093807000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpeter-thiel-argentina-billionaire-moving-abroad-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Peter%20Thiel%20is%20reportedly%20moving%20to%20Argentina%2C%20part%20of%20a%20trend%20among%20billionaires%20looking%20to%20live%20abroad%20as%20they%20hedge%20their%20bets%20on%20the%20US.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mberg%40businessinsider.com%20(Madeline%20Berg%2CBen%20Shimkus)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A93%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Matt%20Walsh%20Slams%20Erika%20Kirk%20Boyfriend%20Rumors%20as%20Blake%20Wynn%20Breaks%20Silence%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1780093587000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131401610%2Cimgsize-2337659.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus-streamers%2Fno-dignity-matt-walsh-erupts-over-erika-kirk-boyfriend-rumor-while-blake-wynn-breaks-silence%2Farticleshow%2F131401645.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mat