%20own%2C%20so%20let%20me%20break%20down%20what%20they%20actually%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuietPort%20and%20CleanBass%20both%20refer%20to%20the%20soundbar's%20ported%20design%2C%20which%20vents%20the%20internal%20tubing.%20This%20helps%20make%20low-frequency%20bass%20less%20skewed%20and%20more%20powerful.%20PhaseGuide%20is%20Bose's%20term%20for%20its%20sound%20projection%20process%2C%20which%20reflects%20audio%20so%20it%20sounds%20like%20there%20are%20virtual%20speakers%20all%20around%20the%20room.%20TrueSpatial%20is%20the%20company's%20immersive%20audio%20processing%2C%20which%20can%20create%20a%20more%20three-dimensional%20soundscape%20from%20stereo%20sources.%20CustomTune%20adjusts%20the%20playback%20to%20your%20room's%20dimensions.%20And%20SpeechClarity%20is%20Bose's%20latest%20AI-assisted%20dialogue%20enhancement%2C%20available%20in%20low%2C%20medium%2C%20and%20high%20settings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20flagship%20soundbars%20from%20other%20brands%20offer%20their%20own%20versions%20of%20those%20features%2C%20so%20on%20paper%2C%20they're%20nothing%20new.%20However%2C%20after%20seeing%20some%20behind-the-scenes%20demos%20and%20experiencing%20the%20soundbar%20in%20my%20home%2C%20Bose's%20approach%20appears%20to%20use%20some%20meaningful%2C%20differentiated%20technology%20under%20the%20hood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close-up%20of%20the%20rear%20of%20a%20Bose%20Lifestyle%20Ultra%20Soundbar%20showing%20its%20wired%20ports.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a19e1bc2ab5f9757add69f0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHDMI%20eARC%2C%20Ethernet%2C%20and%20a%20wired%20subwoofer%20connection%20are%20housed%20on%20the%20back%20of%20the%20soundbar.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20connectivity%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126490979l