rophone%20to%20optimize%20the%20soundbar%20to%20your%20room's%20dimensions%2C%20that%20EQ%20adjustment%20can%20be%20turned%20on%20and%20off.%20It's%20easy%20to%20A%2FB%20test%20the%20sound%20profile%20and%20decide%20which%20you%20prefer.%20Even%20swapping%20the%20rear%20left%20and%20right%20speakers%20is%20a%20single%20button%20press%20in%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227f3387a9-274d-4824-819c-77aabe46d517%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Movie%20performance%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMovies%20sound%20immersive%20and%20dynamic%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Bose%20Lifestyle%20Ultra%20Soundbar%20resting%20on%20our%20reviewer's%20media%20console%20underneath%20their%20TV.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a19e2132ab5f9757add69fa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20soundbar%20delivers%20great%20sound%20quality%2C%20with%20impressive%20simulated%20surround%20sound.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tested%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126490979l-20%26h%3Dd359747106a48368c6cb7f1a385edd31f4fc776c4411669c77ea775dd1f5b991%26postID%3D6a199f25779c116778303739%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fbose-lifestyle-ultra-soundbar-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FBose-Lifestyle-Soundbar-Wireless-Surround%252Fdp%252FB0GLHDQ1FX%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELifestyle%20Ultra%20Soundbar%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20multiple%20ways%2C%20including%20as%20part%20of%20a%20full%20surround%20sound%20system%20with%20two%20rear%20Lifestyle%20Ultra%20Speakers%20and%20a%20Lifestyle%20Ultra%20Subwoofer.%20This%20configuration%20enables%20a%20complete%207.1.4%20experience.%20It%20gets%20unbelievably%20loud%2C%20yet%20remains%20controlled%2C%20like%20being%20in%20a%20theater