E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20the%20most%20immersive%20experience%20possible%2C%20you%20can%20adjust%20the%20soundbar's%20height%20and%20surround%20effects%20in%20the%20Bose%20app.%20Separate%20from%20EQ%2C%20you%20can%20change%20the%20center%2C%20height%2C%20and%20surround%20options%20between%20-10%20and%20%2B10.%20Depending%20on%20the%20movie%20or%20show%2C%20the%20effects%20can%20be%20extremely%20engrossing%2C%20especially%20the%20surround%20option.%20Personally%2C%20I%20preferred%20to%20leave%20these%20set%20to%20zero%2C%20but%20even%20at%20higher%20levels%2C%20they%20didn't%20sound%20overly%20gimmicky%20like%20you%20might%20expect.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20also%20toggle%20on%20SpeechClarity%2C%20which%20Bose%20says%20uses%20AI%20to%20enhance%20on-screen%20dialogue%20without%20dulling%20or%20altering%20other%20sounds.%20In%20my%20testing%2C%20I%20found%20that%20to%20be%20accurate.%20On%20low%2C%20it%20perfectly%20boosts%20dialogue%20just%20a%20touch%2C%20which%20often%20felt%20like%20how%20the%20movie%20should%20have%20been%20mixed%20in%20the%20first%20place.%20Going%20to%20medium%20and%20high%20levels%20sounds%20among%20the%20most%20natural%20of%20any%20%26quot%3Bvoice%20boosting%26quot%3B%20tech%20I've%20heard.%20This%20feature%20alone%20might%20not%20be%20a%20reason%20to%20buy%20this%20soundbar%2C%20but%20it's%20tempting%20if%20you%20often%20have%20trouble%20hearing%20voices%20in%20movies%20and%20TV%20shows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20ran%20Bose's%20CustomTune%20process%20a%20few%20times%20to%20adjust%20the%20soundbar%20to%20my%20environment.%20But%20since%20my%20living%20room%20is%20an%20average-sized%20rectangle%2C%20I%20didn't%20notice%20much%20difference%20when%20I%20toggled%20it%20on%20and%20off.%20Other%20people%20with%20more%20atypical%20room%20designs%20may%20get%20more%20dramatic%20results%2C%20but%20the%20nice%20thing%20is%20that%20you%20aren't%20confined%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ff96e2c8-7098-434c-8223-e3909c344