ghs%20cut%20through%20more%2C%20and%20the%20whole%20sound%20is%20brighter%20than%20Sonos'%20offering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20another%20distinction%20between%20the%20two.%20The%20Sonos%20Arc%20Ultra%20supports%20native%20Dolby%20Atmos%20music%20playback%2C%20while%20the%20Bose%20Lifestyle%20Ultra%20only%20supports%20Atmos%20for%20movies%20and%20TV%20shows.%20With%20native%20Dolby%20Atmos%20playback%2C%20a%20soundbar%20uses%20metadata%20embedded%20in%20the%20music%20track%20by%20the%20recording%20engineers%20to%20place%20sounds%20accurately%20through%20its%20upfiring%20drivers.%20Bose%2C%20by%20contrast%2C%20relies%20on%20its%20own%20TrueSpatial%20processing%20to%20create%20a%20similar%20effect%2C%20deciding%20for%20itself%20how%20to%20position%20the%20different%20elements%20of%20a%20music%20track.%20Though%20Bose's%20TrueSpatial%20tech%20works%20well%20enough%2C%20native%20Atmos%20music%20playback%20would%20be%20more%20accurate%2C%20and%20it's%20odd%20that%20it's%20not%20supported.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I%20wouldn't%20recommend%20spending%20the%20money%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15126490979l-20%26h%3Dd359747106a48368c6cb7f1a385edd31f4fc776c4411669c77ea775dd1f5b991%26postID%3D6a199f25779c116778303739%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Ftech%252Fbose-lifestyle-ultra-soundbar-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FBose-Lifestyle-Soundbar-Wireless-Surround%252Fdp%252FB0GLHDQ1FX%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELifestyle%20Ultra%20Soundbar%3C%2Fa%3E%20just%20as%20a%20music%20speaker%2C%20it%20works%20well%20as%20a%20secondary%20function%20when%20your%20TV%20is%20off.%20The%20volume%20is%20tremendous%2C%20and%20it%20could%20easily%20serve%20as%20a%20party%20speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e4d39a3f-75b8-4308-be2d-23ef7dd2169a%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Cons%20to%20consider%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20con