0traditional%20options%20can%20be.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanchita%20agrees%2C%20warning%20against%20%E2%80%9Chealth%20bars%E2%80%9D%20and%20gummies%20with%20hidden%20sugars.%20%E2%80%9CCheck%20the%20labels.%20Less%20than%20four%20grams%20of%20added%20sugar%2C%20at%20least%20four%20grams%20of%20protein%2C%20and%20no%20strange%20codes%20like%20E422%20or%20INS%20numbers%20%E2%80%94%20that%E2%80%99s%20the%20checklist.%20Once%20parents%20learn%20to%20read%20labels%2C%20half%20the%20battle%20is%20won.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESigns%20that%20the%20nutrition%20plan%20is%20working%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20children%20eat%20better%2C%20the%20results%20go%20beyond%20physical%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201368px)%20100vw%2C%201368px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FFoxtail-Millets-_-Thinai-_-Health-Benefits-%E2%80%93-Buy-Now-At-The-Best-Price-1749577177.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221368%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22In%202019%2C%20the%20Government%20successfully%20lobbied%20for%20the%20United%20Nations%20to%20declare%202023%20as%20the%20International%20Year%20of%20Millets.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FFoxtail-Millets-_-Thinai-_-Health-Benefits-%E2%80%93-Buy-Now-At-The-Best-Price-1749577177.jpg%201368w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FFoxtail-Millets-_-Thinai-_-Health-Benefits-%E2%80%93-Buy-Now-At-The-Best-Price-1749577177-300x168.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FFoxtail-Millets-_-Thinai-_-Health-Benefits-%E2%80%93-Buy-Now-At-The-Best-Price-1749577177-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FFoxtail-Millets-_-Thinai-_-Health-Benefits-%E2%80%93-Buy-Now-At-The-Best-Price-1749577177-768x431.jp